202191.desc: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.
202191.name: Hibiscus Garments

202199.desc: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.
202199.name: Newcastle (Retrofit)

202201.desc: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.
202201.name: White Rose

202202.desc: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?
202202.name: Scorching-Hot Seirios

202203.desc: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?
202203.name: Azure Horizons

202211.desc: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...
202211.name: Eastern Grace

202219.desc: It is my honour to be of everyone's service. Light cruiser Curacoa takes it upon herself to continue serving you, Master.
202219.name: Curacoa (Retrofit)

202221.desc: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.
202221.name: Rhythm of the Dragon Empery

202229.desc: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister, Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.
202229.name: Curlew (Retrofit)

202230.desc: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.
202230.name: Swiftsure

202231.desc: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.
202231.name: Study Hall Cyclamen

202232.desc: I agreed to try on this outfit, but... I know these fancy outfits don't suit me... H-huh, I look gorgeous?! ...Thank you very much. Even if you're just trying to make me feel better, I appreciate it...
202232.name: Beauty of White Jade

202233.desc: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?
202233.name: Midsummer Special Service

202240.desc: Err, you're... the Commander, yes? You don't know who I am? Ah, right, I've yet to introduce myself... I'm Black Prince of the Royal Navy... Will that suffice?
202240.name: Black Prince

202241.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?
202241.name: White Princess

202242.desc: A "qipao," is it? So this legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?
202242.name: Fair Maid Spring

202243.desc: You can't have a party without champagne, right? Now, if I remember right, you're meant to give it a good shake before popping the cork... Oh no! Look out, Commander!
202243.name: Pop the Cork

202244.desc: Oh... Welcome, Commander. Can I take your order...? Or maybe, you just wanted to kick back and relax? ...Either way is fine with me.
202244.name: Addled Attendant?

202250.desc: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.
202250.name: Sheffield μ

202261.desc: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?
202261.name: A Maid in Class

202271.desc: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...
202271.name: Pure White Angel

202272.desc: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.
202272.name: Pure White Holiday

202273.desc: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.
202273.name: Graceful Afternoon Tea

202274.desc: How are you feeling, Commander? Hehe, I'm not wearing my usual nurse's gown right now, but I suppose this isn't much different~
202274.name: Pristine Herbalist

202275.desc: Commander, umm... Happy Valentine's Day! What do you think of my outfit? Hehe, it's perfect for a date, isn't it?
202275.name: Winter Dearest

202278.desc: I'm so happy to have come this far with you, Commander. May this gorgeous sunrise watch over us for all time... I love you, Commander.
202278.name: Dawn's Oath

202280.desc: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!
202280.name: Dido µ

202291.desc: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?
202291.name: Ruby-Red Boudoir

202292.desc: Welcome, welcome. I've been working here as a maid, just as you told me to. Umm... Call for me only when you're ready to order.
202292.name: Salty Maid

202301.desc: *Pats thighs* Master, you poor thing~ Look how hard you've been working~ Hehe, hurry and come here so that I can pamper you~
202301.name: Red Chamber of Healing

202302.desc: Tis a pleasure to see you, Master. I am delighted to be your partner for today. ...Oh, I was just trying to sound prim and proper! You don't need to look at me with such pity in your eyes!
202302.name: Brilliant Belle

202303.desc: As you can see, today's theme... is a seaside pampering, or something like that~ Heehee. I know you're no stranger to the sea, Commander, but today, we're here to play, not work. Just take it easy, and unwind~♪
202303.name: Prim Sea Breeze

202311.desc: My liege... No, excuse me, I should be calling you Master, right? Bellona of the Royal Maids, reporting in. My, you seem quite lost for words... I'll explain the situation to you later, so don't worry about it.
202311.name: Armed to Clean

202331.desc: Did you come all this way just because I asked you to, Master? Or... would you prefer I call you "Senpai" here? If we're at school, then there's no reason for me to act maidly, now is there? Heeheehee♪
202331.name: Femme Fatale Fresher

203010.desc: London-class heavy cruiser – London, Hull Number 69!
203010.name: London

203011.desc: Splendid work today, Your Excellency. Here are your documents for the next mission. It has everything you need to know, so please give it a read. Heehee, I'm happy to assist so that you may focus solely on achieving your goals.
203011.name: The Sterling Secretary

203018.desc: Why are you so astounded, Your Excellency? You expressly requested an unforgettable and elaborate ceremony. Heehee, you'll make it weird if you keep staring so much, so won't you please take my hand now?
203018.name: Platinum Ceremony

203019.desc: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?
203019.name: London (Retrofit)

203020.desc: London-class heavy cruiser – Shropshire, Hull Number 73!
203020.name: Shropshire

203029.desc: As you know, I'm the youngest of London class, Shropshire~ I'm excited to work with you! Heheh, I look pretty capable now, don't I? Maybe I'll cause a little less trouble for you now, Commander!
203029.name: Shropshire (Retrofit)

203030.desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Kent, Hull Number 54!
203030.name: Kent

203040.desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Suffolk, Hull Number 55!
203040.name: Suffolk

203049.desc: Whew... At long last, after all that hard work, I get to wear this uniform as well. Even though all I did was... Huh? Lead by example? Be a role model? I don't get it...
203049.name: Suffolk (Retrofit)

203050.desc: Norfolk-class heavy cruiser - Norfolk, Hull Number 78!
203050.name: Norfolk

203060.desc:
Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40
<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving</color>
203060.name: Dorsetshire

203070.desc: York-class heavy cruiser - York, Hull Number 90!
203070.name: York

203071.desc: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!
203071.name: Truth Seeker

203072.desc: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?
203072.name: Summoner from the Azure Depths

203078.desc: Whoa... Is this my Uniform for the ceremony known as the Oath of Purity? Hohoho... This must be fate. Join me, Commander, and we shall make the world right once more!
203078.name: Oath of Purity

203079.desc: This is no mere Upgrade, this is an Awakening! I will alter the course of fate itself!
203079.name: York (Retrofit)

203080.desc: York-class heavy cruiser - Exeter, Hull Number 68!
203080.name: Exeter

203081.desc: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.
203081.name: A Glorious Toast

203089.desc: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?
203089.name: Exeter (Retrofit)

203090.desc: London-class heavy cruiser, Sussex. Hull Number 96.
203090.name: Sussex

203091.desc: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?
203091.name: Sunlit Tulips

203092.desc: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...
203092.name: Wine and Red Roses

204011.desc: This Dragon Empery dress is lovely and graceful, but the slit... Commander? I'm sorry if this is sudden, but... how do you like my dress?
204011.name: Graceful Royal Pride

204031.desc: What a feast for sore eyes. I feel great~! Vacations really should be at the beach! Let's show Sara your beach ball, Cygnet!
204031.name: Lady of the Shining Sun

204032.desc: Thank you for inviting me on this wonderful trip. Now that I have donned this beautiful outfit, shall we partake of a Sakura Empire tea party– leisurely and elegantly?
204032.name: Porcelain Grace

204033.desc: Beauty is not always over the rainbow. Sometimes it is right in your backyard. Commander, how would you like to spend this quiet, lovely day right here with me?
204033.name: Dawnlight's Dame

204034.desc: Whoa, there... There you are, Commander. You could have waited at the clubhouse... Why yes, the view is just beautiful, isn't it? Hahaha, thank you for bringing me here today.
204034.name: Gentlewoman and Stallion

204038.desc: If the smooth path only allows one person to travel at a time, then I’ll gladly walk the path not taken with you hand-in-hand.
204038.name: Rosey Love Poem

205010.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Queen Elizabeth, Hull Number 00!
205010.name: Queen Elizabeth

205011.desc: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!
205011.name: The Queen's Ball

205012.desc: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!
205012.name: One Night of the Queen

205013.desc: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪
205013.name: Queen of the Campus

205014.desc: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!
205014.name: Crown Jewel of the Royal Navy

205015.desc: Warspite, what in the world is all this... The Maid Team has to sift through all this paperwork?! I'm tired already... I wish I never mentioned wanting to experience what it's like to be a maid... And you, stop staring and help me already, servant!
205015.name: Yes, Your Maidness!

205016.desc: Servant, what do you think you're doing?! Instead of wasting your life working, go have some fun in the sea for once! We went out of our way to come to the beach, so do not disappoint me!
205016.name: Seaside Orders

205020.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!
205020.name: Warspite

205021.desc: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!
205021.name: Christmas Warrior

205022.desc: We have the finest equipment. Now to turn in a performance worthy of Her Majesty's beauty... Behold, the Royal Stage!
205022.name: Under Pleasure

205029.desc: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!
205029.name: Warspite (Retrofit)

205031.desc: This is such a weird costume… oh well, it’s Halloween after all. It cannot be so bad, this is a fun activity after all. First things first, I didn’t say that I would join from the very beginning!
205031.name: Luna Witch

205032.desc: Hey, are you even enjoying yourself? At least pretend to have fun when I went out of my way to invite you, or else I'm going to lose sleep over this! ...Look behind me? What are you– Oh...!
205032.name: Azure & Gold Summer Night

205039.desc: H-hey, are you sleeping all day, or what? My retrofit is all done. Hmph, you might've widened the gap between us, but... I'm gonna keep on pushing my limits! Got it?
205039.name: Nelson (Retrofit)

205041.desc: Although it's a gift from the Commander, it's still embarrassing to wear this....Commander, do you think you could teach me how to swim?
205041.name: Future Seaside Admiral

205043.desc: Miss Akashi, shall I look at the camera next? Understood. Oh, Commander, I did not expect you to grace us with your presence here as well! Yes, the photoshoot is proceeding smoothly. By the way, is there a favorite pose you'd like to see?
205043.name: Immaculate Beauty

205048.desc: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~
205048.name: Palace of Blessings

205050.desc: King George V-class battleship – King George V.
205050.name: King George V

205051.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~
205051.name: Rose's Regalia

205060.desc: King George V-class battleship – Prince of Wales, Hull Number 53!
205060.name: Prince of Wales

205061.desc: I'm not a big fan of beach volleyball, but Hood begged me... I swear, that girl! She just can't get enough of the sun! You've got to cheer for me!
205061.name: Sun Shining Upon Windsor

205062.desc: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?
205062.name: Sakura Elegance

205064.desc: Oh, Commander. Worry not. Since I've been given this job, I will see through it until the end. Besides, it's been a while since I've gotten this fired up. Haha!
205064.name: The Laureate's Victory Lap

205065.desc: I expected you sooner, Commander. I decided to practice the saxophone while I had some time alone... You shouldn't keep a lady waiting in the future. Heehee. Anyway, I suppose we could listen to a song before we set off, no?
205065.name: A Knight's Song, a Lady's Night

205070.desc: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.
205070.name: Duke of York

205072.desc: Ahh, this luscious scent... comes from thee. What dost thee feel when gazing upon my new dress? Hehe... your lips may lie but your eyes do not...
205072.name: Eternal Night's Carola

205073.desc: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~
205073.name: Prestige of the Glorious Formula

205090.desc: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)
205090.name: Howe

205091.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.
205091.name: Noble Rouge

205092.desc: "Please, Master, save meee." ...Ugh, I can't get into the role. What sort of tone should I be aiming for, love?
205092.name: Pastry Princess

205093.desc: Thanks for your patience, love. I've looked forward to this evening's party for a long, long time. Hopefully George, York, and company won't laugh at me after how much effort I've put into this ensemble... What do you think of it, Commander?
205093.name: Evening Marvels

205101.desc: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!
205101.name: Mischievous Little Nurse

205102.desc: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!
205102.name: Queen Valiant I

205111.desc: Hrmm... *sigh*... Looks like I bungled this one too... I sure hope the Commander doesn't see me like th– Hwuh?! C-Commander? P-please give me a moment! I'll straighten this out right away... Waaah!!
205111.name: The Maid-Knight Charges Forth!

205131.desc: "Please let me know if you need anything, Master"... I'm starting to think you're making me wear this as a sick joke. The reason being, I am obviously NOT fit to be a Royal Maid... Even if I do adore their uniforms...
205131.name: Half-Hearted Masquerade

205141.desc: Commander? Oh, what a coincidence... Were you slacking– err, I mean, taking a break, too? I can make some room for you if you'd like?
205141.name: Bashful Oak

206010.desc: Hermes-class aircraft carrier – Hermes, Hull Number 95!
206010.name: Hermes

206019.desc: Our glory coalesces into the bonds that forge a bright new future! Let's rev it up! Hermes, retrofit complete!
206019.name: Hermes (Retrofit)

206021.desc: Yaaawn... Umm, did I doze off again? Oh no... Organising school events gets so hectic I always end up working right up until curfew... Just give me one more minute, please...
206021.name: A Hundred Sleepless Eyes

206022.desc: "Gaze upon this glorious dress. Admire its brilliance, tremble, and..." If you don't mind, would you please take Argus' hand?
206022.name: Cerulean Enthrallment

206030.desc: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!
206030.name: Unicorn

206031.desc: Unicorn... is now a songstress... *giggles* Unicorn's song has reached Onii-chan's heart.
206031.name: Little Star Songstress

206032.desc: This... present... is for you... I hope you like it... What? Me wearing this outfit is the best gift I can give you? Co... Commander!...
206032.name: The Gift of Spring

206033.desc: Ah, big brother, you're here... Ehehe, I only just got here as well. Um... shall we go then? I kind of... want to go to the amusement park...
206033.name: Long-Awaited Date

206034.desc: So this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire... Changing into it is difficult but... if you like it, then Unicorn is happy!
206034.name: Prayer of Plum and Snow

206035.desc: So I'm... an "idol" now... I'm not sure how well I'll do... But I'll give it my all...!
206035.name: Angelic Night

206036.desc: Oh, big brother... Unicorn is reading right now. Mm, yeah, while eating ice cream... Big brother, want to have a bite?
206036.name: Icy-Sweet Storytime

206037.desc: Unicorn... is now serving as a nurse. Umm... Big brother, would you mind being Unicorn's patient...?
206037.name: Angelic Nurse

206038.desc: This is... an important outfit for an important ceremony... yes! Unicorn and Yuni are both ready for this! Big brother... how do I look?
206038.name: A Dream of Pure Vows

206039.desc: Unicorn has finished her retrofit... Now she can do more for you and her friends!
206039.name: Unicorn (Retrofit)

206041.desc: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?
206041.name: Beachside Undine

206042.desc: I never imagined you would give me such a splendid dress, Commander... I think it's called a "qipao..." is it? I'll try it, revealing though it is. Wh- what do you think...? Do I look... nice?
206042.name: Sprightly Spring Wind

206051.desc: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~
206051.name: The Way of the Dragon Empery

206052.desc: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪
206052.name: Gamer Style

206060.desc: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)
206060.name: Perseus

206061.desc: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?
206061.name: Unfamiliar Duties

206062.desc: Whew. Lunar New Year... Easy to grasp in various ways. Both the holiday and your tastes, I mean. Heehee.
206062.name: Spring's Lackadaisical Leisure

206071.desc: Ah, umm... If you keep staring at me like that... Oh, um, Commander, this is supposed to be a Royalty of the Night costume, right? In that case... Would you mind kneeling for me first?
206071.name: Silvermoon Faerie Princess

206072.desc: Hand brushing my hair behind my ear, eyes toward the camera... Mm, filming promotional material isn't easy... Commander, will this do?
206072.name: Scent of Spring in the Red Pavilion

206081.desc: Steaming hot manjuu buns, ready to be served! Let us have a big feast then gather rosebuds, Commander. Oh, a "holiday gathering" doesn't involve literal gathering?
206081.name: New Year's White Plumage

207010.desc: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)
207010.name: Eagle

207011.desc: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.
207011.name: Eagle's Clinic

207020.desc: Aircraft carrier – Ark Royal, Hull Number 91!
207020.name: Ark Royal

207021.desc: Nothing says summer like the sun, the beach, and destroyers... Ahem! Th-that's right! Even though we're relaxing, we still have to keep an eye out for enemy destroyers! Commander, I may be in a swimsuit, but I'm ready to sortie at any time!
207021.name: Coast Watcher

207022.desc: One tends to let her guard down at a party like this, but worry not! Put the ball in my hands and let Ark Royal keep you safe!
207022.name: Guardian of the Ball

207023.desc: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.
207023.name: New Year's Protectress

207024.desc: This is the place, Commander. What are you going to order? Me, I think I'll have the same as you... Yeah, so what? I just felt like grabbing a coffee with you for once.
207024.name: Café Lookout

207028.desc: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!
207028.name: Pure-White Protector

207029.desc: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!
207029.name: Ark Royal (Retrofit)

207030.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87!
207030.name: Illustrious

207031.desc: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?
207031.name: Never-Ending Tea Party

207032.desc: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~
207032.name: Illustrious Ball

207033.desc: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?
207033.name: Resplendent Hibiscus

207035.desc: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...
207035.name: Maiden Lily's Radiance

207036.desc: A gentle melody for a peaceful celebration. Today, Commander, I offer this tune to you and the people of the port. May my melody please your ears♪
207036.name: Lambent Melody

207038.desc: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.
207038.name: Morning Star of Love and Hope

207041.desc: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!
207041.name: The Goddess' Day Off

207042.desc: Are you preparing to hold an event for the port? Hehe, sounds like you could use my help. Don't worry, with someone as beautiful as me around, anything you do will surely be blessed with success!
207042.name: Guidance of the Spring Goddess

207043.desc: *Yaaawn*... Basking in the autumnal night's wind while gazing at the moon is the very definition of elegance, is it not? Heehee. Right now, I am not acting as a Lady of the Royal Navy, but rather as an "ojou" of the Sakura Empire elegantly enjoying her tea... Hyeep! Hot?!
207043.name: Upon Nights Brisk and Beautiful

207051.desc: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.
207051.name: The Lady of the Beach

207052.desc: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.
207052.name: Timeless Classics

207060.desc: Courageous-class aircraft carrier – Glorious, Hull Number 77.
207060.name: Glorious

207061.desc: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?
207061.name: Glorious School Life

207062.desc: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!
207062.name: Pungent Plum

207071.desc: Oh my... It seems I've shown you a rather unseemly side of me. Would you help me clean up here, Commander? You know... before any of the other girls find out. Heehee~♥
207071.name: Shepherd of the "Lost"

207090.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87.
207090.name: Little Illustrious

207110.desc: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?
207110.name: Illustrious μ

207121.desc: *Sigh*... I thought changing into maid attire would break up the monotony, but just getting into these clothes has tired me out... Oh, Commander? You came at a good time. Shall we slack off together?
207121.name: Ms. Motivationless Maid

213010.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!
213010.name: Erebus

213011.desc: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.
213011.name: Illusory Happiness

213012.desc: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?
213012.name: Wardrobe Witchery

213020.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Terror, Hull Number I03!
213020.name: Terror

213021.desc: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?
213021.name: Halloween Terror

213040.desc: Roberts-class monitor - Abercrombie. Hull Number F109.
213040.name: Abercrombie

213041.desc: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!
213041.name: Pumpkin Blast!

213042.desc: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~
213042.name: Mischief on the Rocks

231210.desc: Tadah! I've got a banquet dress! Heehee~ I decided to go with something refined and voguish this time, as opposed to cute! I mean, it's a dress fit for a banquet, so I think it makes me look pretty grown-up.
231210.name: A Different Dance

236030.desc: Big brother...? I was just practicing my trumpet, if you were wondering... Umm, what do you think? I hope you like my trumpeting...
236030.name: Blissful Movement

299011.desc: Hehe~ I usually let the other girls have all the glory, but even I must sometimes give you something to remember me by. Merry Christmas, Commander~
299011.name: Princess of the Reindeers

299012.desc: Welcome to our celebration, Commander. At this breathtaking venue, I, Neptune, shall be the one to show you around, rather than the Royal Maids. Heehee~♪
299012.name: Nereid's Invitation

299021.desc: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?
299021.name: White Warrick

299022.desc: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.
299022.name: Black Gerard

299031.desc: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!
299031.name: Summery Date!

299032.desc: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...
299032.name: Cait Sith Crooner

299033.desc: "Owner~ I've come to take you to the ball~" ...That's exactly what you were going to do? Eh, doesn't matter who does it~ All that matters is we'll be there together~♪
299033.name: The Cat and the White Steed

299041.desc: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?
299041.name: The Golden Hind's Respite

299051.desc: Rejoice, Commander. I have no doubt that this refreshing sensation will bring you the utmost satisfaction. Come, let us enjoy this experience together.
299051.name: Heart-Throbbing Refreshment

301011.desc: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!
301011.name: 5 Minutes Till I'm Late

301012.desc: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...
301012.name: Mascot Bucky

301013.desc: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?
301013.name: Music Pixy

301014.desc: The whole world's going to feel the tremors from my debut! I'm Fubuki, the Special-type idol!
301014.name: Fubuki Halation!

301015.desc: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...
301015.name: Stormy Waitress-in-Training!

301020.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number two – Shirayuki.
301020.name: Shirayuki

301021.desc: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!
301021.name: Bunny Breeder

301040.desc: Special Type I Fubuki-class destroyer number four – Miyuki.
301040.name: Miyuki

301041.desc: Commander, I think the goods over here are a bit cheaper... Umm, I'm doing fine on my budget still, so we can pick out some more things to buy. A-also, I'll get to spend more time shopping with you... Ah, d-disregard that please... *blushes*
301041.name: Shopping Rendezvous

301042.desc: C-Commander, I'm ready any time... You think my outfit's cute...? Th-thank you... Heheh, I got it just for our date... Umm, I figured hiding my bandages might help ward off my bad luck...
301042.name: Clear Skies and Crepes

301050.desc: First ship of special Type II {namecode:6} class destroyers, {namecode:6}.
301050.name: Ayanami

301051.desc: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?
301051.name: Witch in Ambush

301053.desc: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?
301053.name: Rock 'n' Demon

301054.desc: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?
301054.name: Lunar Demon

301055.desc: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?
301055.name: Grade A Sailor Uniform

301056.desc: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...
301056.name: Covert Ops Cloak

301057.desc: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?
301057.name: Low-Key Idol @Confused

301058.desc: This dress is... {namecode:6}’s. I'm not used to this dress yet... Commander, do you think it fits me?
301058.name: Demon's Finest Dress

301059.desc: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...
301059.name: Ayanami (Retrofit)

301091.desc: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!
301091.name: Akatsuki Goes North

301092.desc: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!
301092.name: Motoninja Akatsuki

301093.desc: Look out! Move, Commander! ...Phew. To explain, I am helping Santa give out Christmas presents! Now excuse me, I cannot tarry here or I'll be late... Wait, have I come to the wrong place? WHAT?!
301093.name: Santa's Lost Helper!

301094.desc: Welcome, Commander, to DesDiv 6's tent of entertainment! For our first act, I shall perform for you my most stunning ninjutsu! ..."Circus"? I've never heard of this word before!
301094.name: Cirque de Ninjutsu!

301100.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number two – Hibiki.
301100.name: Hibiki

301101.desc: New Year's finally comes to port! I, Hibiki of the 6th DesDiv, will be marking my new arrival in my New Year's attire! Commander, don't you dare change the channel - you've gotta watch my every move~!
301101.name: New Year's Little Imp

301110.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number three - Ikazuchi.
301110.name: Ikazuchi

301111.desc: {namecode:13}, {namecode:13} has been transformed into tea! What should we do! {namecode:14} and {namecode:13} will get slurped up by the Commander!
301111.name: Sakura Tea

301112.desc: Inazuma and I have been to a lot of festivals together, but this would be the first time that I've gone with you, Commander. Isn't this totally like a date?
301112.name: Thunderous Festival

301113.desc: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?
301113.name: Dawn's Thunder

301114.desc: Commander, I've worn what you asked me to– Oh, I see, I see. So this is what they call a "maid kink," right? Is that what you're into now, Commander?
301114.name: Courtyard Maid Ikazuchi

301120.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number four - Inazuma.
301120.name: Inazuma

301121.desc: It doesn’t matter if {namecode:14} becomes Mr. Commander's dessert… but if {namecode:14} cannot be found, Mr. Commander will feel so devastated, perhaps he won’t be able to command the fleet… so… please! Please convey {namecode:14}'s heartfelt wish to Mr. Commander——
301121.name: Vanilla Pudding

301122.desc: I usually go to festivals with Ikazuchi, but this would be my first time going with you. Hmm? Where should we visit first?
301122.name: Flash of Fireworks

301123.desc: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?
301123.name: Dusk's Lightning

301131.desc: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!
301131.name: Is The Order A Torpedo?

301141.desc: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!
301141.name: Shogun of Snowballs

301143.desc: Commander, look at me, look at me! What do you think of my new outfit? If you like it, wanna give it a feel?
301143.name: Carnivore Carnival!

301144.desc: Christmas! The day Santa Claus drops by and leaves presents, right? Hell yeah, I'm pumped! Aren't you pumped too, Commander?
301144.name: Woofy Floofy Christmas Night

301148.desc: Commander, look! Look at this new dress. Red and white, I really really like it! But what's the occasion?
301148.name: The Bride of Solomon

301149.desc: Woof...? Am I imagining it, or did you get shorter, Commander? Unless... it's me who's gotten bigger? Seriously?! Nobody told me retrofitting makes you taller!
301149.name: Yuudachi (Retrofit)

301151.desc: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?
301151.name: Attack, I-490!

301152.desc: Oh my. Commander, you must be pretty lucky to bump into me here, hehe~ Since you're here, you can have the privilege of being my escort tonight. Now, be grateful~♪
301152.name: The Ballroom's Lucky Star

301153.desc: All right, that should be good... Hey, stupid Commander standing around aimlessly. Yeah, you. Stick your hand out. You're gonna be the first person to get MY chocolate, so I'd better see some tears of gratitude.
301153.name: Lucky Chocolate

301159.desc: Heheh~ Retrofitting the mighty Shigure proves that you are quite perceptive! Aren't you glad that you get to rely on me more, you lucky idiot of a commander~♪
301159.name: Shigure (Retrofit)

301161.desc: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!
301161.name: Sovereign of the Swing

301162.desc: Wa ha ha~! Did your heart skip a beat from seeing the charming Yukikaze? Hmph... Well, looks like the Dragon Empery girls are setting off firecrackers... let's go join them! Here, make sure to hold on to my hand!
301162.name: Winter's Snowy Wind

301168.desc: This outfit is sooo cute~ ehehe... Ack!! *cough* *cough*! Ahem! From now on, you are the faithful companion of Yukikaze the Great! As such, you will not be permitted to leave my side, understood?
301168.name: The Warmth of Spring

301171.desc: Commander, trick or treat! I expect you to give some candy to my sisters as well! These will-o'-wisps? Hahaha~ I tried imitating that gloomy sister of mine!
301171.name: Pumpkins and Festivities!

301179.desc: The newly-retrofitted Kagerou has arrived~ I won't let that sister of mine pass me up anymore! Commander, lead us forward towards distant shores!
301179.name: Kagerou (Retrofit)

301181.desc: I see a chance... to capitalize on the Dragon Empery's famous mooncakes... Commander, would you like to have a taste of the Moon Palace's delicacies? If you buy them in bulk, I'll give you a special discount.
301181.name: Mooncake Merchant

301189.desc: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...
301189.name: Shiranui (Retrofit)

301211.desc: Everyone's playing together...? I-I think I'll pass... Y-you want me to join them? Ugh, well, if you say so, then I-I-I'll try to socialize with them...!
301211.name: Snow Day Hatsuharu

301212.desc: C-Commander, I will be your partner for the party tonight. Let's see, umm... I believe this is proper Royal Navy etiquette... D-did I do it correctly?
301212.name: Hatsuharu in the Limelight

301213.desc: U-umm... In order to conquer shyness, umm, I've come to serve you... I just hope I don't get in everyone's way... Y-yeah! Thank you for your encouraging words! I'll do my best...!
301213.name: Hatsuharu's Cat Café Caper

301219.desc: Hatsuharu, retrofit complete... H-hopefully I'm a little bit stronger now...
301219.name: Hatsuharu (Retrofit)

301231.desc: Yaho~ Good morning, Commander! For a limited time only, Wakaba Claus will be delivering Christmas presents! Huh? My bag? Aaahhh! C-Commander, help me pick everything up!
301231.name: Holiday Special Wakaba!

301232.desc: Hmmgh! Oh yeah... Ah, there you are, Commander! Care to join me? Come bask in the afternoon sunshine, it feels great!
301232.name: A Healthy Dose of Sunshine!

301242.desc: Cheers, Commander~ C'mere, you've got to enjoy the party too! If you're thinking of doing something tactless like running off to go back to work, people are going to get upset with you~
301242.name: Perennial Joy

301249.desc: Hatsushimo's retrofitting is complete. You don't think I look all that different? Oh, Commander, you're still as simple as ever~ I've changed in tons of ways beyond what's just on the surface. Heheheh~
301249.name: Hatsushimo (Retrofit)

301251.desc: Hope everyone enjoys the oodles of balloons I made for this party! Yeah, I'm sure the little girls will love 'em!
301251.name: Unending Friendship

301259.desc: Ah... So this is what it feels like to be retrofitted. I'll work harder for your sake, and for everyone in the 27th Destroyer Division~
301259.name: Ariake (Retrofit)

301261.desc: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!
301261.name: Maid-In-Training!

301262.desc: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. Commander, what do you think?
301262.name: Twilight Blossom

301263.desc: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?
301263.name: Evening Flower

301264.desc: Woah... These stalls have all sorts of amazing things~ Commander, will you help me pick a gift out for Ariake? Hm, let's see... How about this Daruma doll?
301264.name: Summer Festival Shopping

301265.desc: I was really looking forward to playing with you at the beach, Commander, so I changed into this swimsuit. Umm... Ariake told me that I had to choose something that was easy to move around in, and cute enough to make you lose your mind... Was she pulling my leg?
301265.name: Fun in the Sun

301269.desc: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.
301269.name: Yuugure (Retrofit)

301291.desc: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!
301291.name: World's Speediest Bunny Waitress

301292.desc: Whoa-whoa-whoa! Why'd I end up here again?! Even though I've been running for a whole hour! ...Commander?! Waaaah, I'm so glad to see you! Please, help me get out of heeeeeeere!
301292.name: The White Rabbit of Wonderland

301293.desc: You can't keep sprinting across the sea forever. Sometimes, you need to rest and recover your strength. Speaking of, you may use my parasol if you like, Commander!
301293.name: The Island Wind Rests

301294.desc: Oh no! Commander, look out! ...Phew. That was really close. Apologies for my clear lack of attentiveness! I shouldn't have been in such a rush to deliver all these mooncakes...
301294.name: Clumsy Moon Rabbit

301309.desc: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~
301309.name: Kamikaze (Retrofit)

301319.desc: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~
301319.name: Matsukaze (Retrofit)

301321.desc: Commander, Merry Christmas~! I am on my best behavior today as well! Uuu... when is Santa Claus going to come? I'm sleepy...
301321.name: Mr. Reindeer, Depart!

301322.desc: Comainder, I put on my yukata just like you said! Ehehe, you should take me to the festival so I can get lots and lots of candy!
301322.name: Candy Festival!

301323.desc: I heard that if I go around telling people "Happy New Year," I can get lots of goodies! Ehehe, I hope they'll give me a bunch of candy!
301323.name: Spring Festival Sweets

301329.desc: Comainder, I'm done retrofitting! Have some candy! Hm? You're always nice to me, so I'm giving you some candy!
301329.name: Mutsuki (Retrofit)

301331.desc: Co... commander, {namecode:34}'s new outfit... How does it look? It's a new year... {namecode:34} wants to keep improving...
301331.name: New Year's Wish

301339.desc: Kisaragi... retrofitting complete... I want to be able to help everyone out more...
301339.name: Kisaragi (Retrofit)

301350.desc: The fourth ship of {namecode:33} class destroyer — {namecode:137}
301350.name: Uzuki

301351.desc: Ah... Big sis {namecode:34}, big sis {namecode:33}, let's sleep together... Commander? You want to come too?
301351.name: Sleepy Uzuki

301381.desc: Huh...? Where am I...? What time is it...?
301381.name: Sleepy Fairy

301391.desc: Nagatsuki the kitty maid is at your service~ Do your best to not fall madly in love with my cute looks~! Hehe~
301391.name: Dangerous Kitty Maid?

301411.desc: Mikazuki is supposed to be... a jiangshi? Um... hip... hop... Commander, trick or treaaaaat~
301411.name: Sweet Zombie

301471.desc: What's the matter, Commander? Oh, this outfit? ...Um, I heard that this outfit would bring you therapeutic benefits and hoped to try it on... Wh-what do you think? Does it feel therapeutic to you?
301471.name: Soft and Fluffy Therapy

301472.desc: Commander, it is my pleasure to accompany you today. Umm... What do you think? I decided to go for a different outfit this time... D-do you think it's cute?
301472.name: Baby Steps

301481.desc: Voilà! Don't go anywhere, Commander! My magic show will start in just a sec! To start with, let's hear a roar! Roooaar!
301481.name: Now for a Magic Trick!

301491.desc: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...
301491.name: Monochromatic Interlude

301498.desc: This must be the dream you've awaited so eagerly... Of course, I vowed to be with you until the end of our days. I shall take my rightful place beside you and your ideals. We are... together.
301498.name: Unsullied White Fox

301541.desc: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...
301541.name: Festive Riding Hood?

301571.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?
301571.name: A Dance for the Coming Spring

301581.desc: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.
301581.name: Sports Festival Preparations

301582.desc: Mmh... Happy New Year. I'm working on hooking my friends up with these firecrackers... The bun I'm eating? I received it as a thank-you for my efforts.
301582.name: Firecrackers and Steamed Buns

301591.desc: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!
301591.name: Seasonal Shogun

301592.desc: Ugh... Even though we finally got all our gear, we still need more band members... Commander! Stop complaining and come hither! From now on, you're a member of the Sengoku Shredders!
301592.name: Sengoku☆Shredder!

301601.desc: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!
301601.name: New Year's Campaign

301602.desc: General! I, Isokaze, have done my utmost to prepare the equipment! Now, with Lord Urakaze's presence, our Sengoku☆War-Band is complete! Of course, you are more than welcome to join our ranks, General!
301602.name: Sengoku☆Smasher!

301611.desc: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?
301611.name: The Honors Student

301612.desc: I'm experimenting with different flavors since we're running a pop-up café... Alright! I think I'll go with this one! Strap in, Commander, because you're about to do a lot of taste-testing!
301612.name: The Secret Ingredient is Love?!

301619.desc: Commander, have you been having more fun since I arrived? ... I see, that's great! Ehehe... Hamakaze, getting hyped!
301619.name: Hamakaze (Retrofit)

301621.desc: Little butterfly, little butterfly... Ya! It flew away... {namecode:128}~ {namecode:128}~ Where are you? {namecode:142}? {namecode:143}? We said we were going to play at the seaside. Where is everyone?
301621.name: Lost Girl and Labyrinth Butterfly

301622.desc: Commander, I'm mopping the floor right now. Please watch your step, as it's quite slippery over there... Eek! Owch... I suppose I should've watched my own step... Ahaha...
301622.name: Sparkly-Clean

301629.desc: I'm {namecode:127}, blowing and blustering from the mountaintop! Whoa! Butterflies? Butterflies?! Look, butterflies! For me? Thanks, Commander!
301629.name: {namecode:127} (Retrofit)

301631.desc: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.
301631.name: The Transfer Student Underneath the Dancing Petals

301632.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?
301632.name: Snow-Dusted Lynx Tips

301633.desc: Commander, thank you for coming to see me. I'm currently rehearsing my program for the Spring Festival performance. I do hope it is to your liking.
301633.name: Robes of Dancing Clouds

301641.desc: Merry Christmas~ Commander, we gotta go hand out presents to them destroyers~ You be Santa, I'll be yer reindeer~
301641.name: The Reindeer's Present

301642.desc: Happy anniversary~ Today's a day to enjoy to yer heart's content, ya know? I'm just havin' fun in my own way, checkin' out cute girls from afar~ I appreciate yer concern though, Commander~
301642.name: Woozy Party

301643.desc: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~
301643.name: Bringer of Fortunes

301644.desc: Finally we're through with them mornin' classes~ Commander, would ya fancy havin' lunch with me? Heheh, yer wonderin' what I done made? You'll see for yerself soon 'nuff~
301644.name: Let's 'ave Lunch

301651.desc: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!
301651.name: Fluttering Fanfare

301661.desc: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?
301661.name: The Gentlest Firework

301720.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number 10 – Uranami.
301720.name: Uranami

301721.desc: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!
301721.name: Snow Vanguard

301801.desc: All right, everything looks good! I'm super excited and my batteries are fully charged! I'm heading out~!
301801.name: Time for School!

301811.desc: Warm and comforting clothes... Warm and comforting red bean soup... Ahh, I love New Year's.
301811.name: New Year's Comfort

301812.desc: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?
301812.name: At School with Foo

301819.desc: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.
301819.name: Kasumi (Retrofit)

301821.desc: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~
301821.name: Morning Moon, Beachside Flower

301822.desc: What kinds of flowers should I decorate the office with for the Lunar New Year...? Ugh, I just can't decide! Um, Commander, will you be inspecting the interior? I'll show you around! Phew...
301822.name: Blossoming Spring, Resplendent Moon

301831.desc: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?
301831.name: Long Waves of Happiness

301832.desc: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...
301832.name: Long-Awaited Warmth

301833.desc: I wanted to help you relieve some stress, so I thought I would read some folk tales to you... When I mentioned that, Akashi suggested these clothes to me... Wh-what do you think?
301833.name: Nestling Up for the Long Nights

301838.desc: Now that the big day is here, I'm awfully nervous... I-I'll be in your care now and forever, okay?
301838.name: Waves of Eternal Love

301841.desc: Commander, over here! We're about to start without you! Ahaha, what would you like to do, Commander? Beach volleyball? Sandcastle building? We can also go relax in the water if you'd like!
301841.name: Suzutsuki, Beachside Attendant!

301842.desc: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!
301842.name: Suzutsuki, Hanetsuki Adept!

301851.desc: Commander, have you also come to play on the beach? You're telling me to be careful? Hmph, what misfortune could possibly befall me from a game of watermelon splitting... Gwaah?!
301851.name: Summer Dedication

301852.desc: Happy New Year to you, Commander. To celebrate the season, I had these garments tailor-made for me, using traditional Dragon Empery clothes as a basis. I don't look... childish, do I?
301852.name: Jet Ink, Silver Quills

301861.desc: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.
301861.name: After-School Melody

301862.desc: *lick*... Oh, Commander, y-you're here for the fireworks? ...Want to watch them with me, then? I've got drinks. My ice cream? Umm... You can't have it.
301862.name: Placid Waves, Passionate Heart

301863.desc: I'm doing lots of training. Gardening, making tea, stuff like that. Here's an example... Umm, do you want dinner, or a bath, or... Hm? I shouldn't practice that one?
301863.name: Diligent Domestic Discipline

301881.desc: Oh nooo! Look out, Commander! ...Oh, phew... I'm glad I didn't mess up your clothes because of my carelessness! Please forgive me for my blunder! I'll clean the floor up right away!
301881.name: Slapdash Blue Sparrow

301882.desc: Blue Sparrow Wakatsuki is here! ...Commander, why are you just staring—Oh, no! I'm caught on the curtain... Aaaah!
301882.name: Blue Sparrow Heralding Spring

301891.desc: Peace~♪ Do I look good in the pic? Don't I look so adorable you'll never wanna delete the photo, and have to stare at it every day to feel at ease? Heehee♪
301891.name: August's First Romance

301901.desc: *yaaawn*... Goodness me, there I go falling asleep. You understand how pleasant the sea breeze is, don't you? YOU calling ME a slacker!
301901.name: Lulled by Rough Seas

302019.desc: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!
302019.name: Yuubari (Retrofit)

302040.desc: First ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:46}.
302040.name: Nagara

302041.desc: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~
302041.name: Spring Breeze Leisure

302050.desc: Second ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:48}.
302050.name: Isuzu

302051.desc: There will be lots and lots of ghosts and spirits during Halloween... I, I’m not afraid!... say, can, can you hold my hand?
302051.name: Night of Fairy Tale

302052.desc: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...
302052.name: Cozy Christmas Eve

302053.desc: Wooah! ...I fell down again... But at least it's cooler now... Huh? A photoshoot? Noo, don't take a picture of me~
302053.name: Accidental Overheat?

302054.desc: W-w-woah! W-wait up! You guys are going too fast! I'm gonna fall! I'm gonna faaaaall! You're supposed to carry me in a way that doesn't give me a heart attack!! Commander, something crazy seems to have happened with my cavalry~!!
302054.name: Charge, My Trusty Steeds!

302059.desc: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!
302059.name: Isuzu (Retrofit)

302061.desc: Mmfhuhu~♡ What's the matter, Commander? Enraptured by my charms? Heehee, you're frozen in place! You can't begin to think of how to compliment me, can you? "Enough staring, out with the compliments!"
302061.name: Beach Paradise

302070.desc: Nagara-class light cruiser number four – Yura.
302070.name: Yura

302071.desc: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?
302071.name: We are Succubi?

302080.desc: I'm Kinu. If you want this demon to do your bidding, then you'd better show me what you're capable of!
302080.name: Kinu

302081.desc: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.
302081.name: New Year's Blade Demon

302082.desc: Well? I've still got one card in my hand. If you want to win, then show me everything you've got! I will not have you disrespect me just for wearing a silly costume!
302082.name: Token and Ghost

302089.desc: Retrofit complete... Look forward to commanding the might of the demon ascended. I shall not disappoint you!
302089.name: Kinu (Retrofit)

302090.desc: Sixth ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:47}.
302090.name: Abukuma

302099.desc: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!
302099.name: Abukuma (Retrofit)

302109.desc: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.
302109.name: Mogami (Retrofit)

302110.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.
302110.name: Mikuma

302111.desc: Commander, may you and all our friends enjoy peace and good health... Alright, what did you think? That was a ceremonial dance I'd like to offer to everyone at the main event.
302111.name: Offerings of Floral Grace

302120.desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number one – Sendai.
302120.name: Sendai

302129.desc: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?
302129.name: Sendai (Retrofit)

302131.desc: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don’t you come out and get some fresh air as well?
302131.name: The Tactician's Vacation

302132.desc: "Where do you think you're going so early in the morning, Little Red Riding Hood?" ...Oh, if it isn't the Commander. This might be my own little whim, but I often find myself thinking the same way as this character... If you don't mind, I'd like to hear your feedback about my acting.
302132.name: The Gray Wolf's Ploy

302139.desc: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.
302139.name: Jintsuu (Retrofit)

302140.desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number three – Naka.
302140.name: Naka

302141.desc: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?
302141.name: Foxy Summer Surfer

302200.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.
302200.name: Agano

302201.desc: Even though I'm not really into this whole "Christmas" thing, if it means I get to toy around with your heart by wearing this cute outfit of mine, then I suppose I would be interested. Hehe~
302201.name: Christmas Eve Tease

302202.desc: "Oh my, you're also out for a stroll? Hehe, my name's Agano. And what might yours be?" ...Jeez, Commander, take this more seriously. According to the setting, we just met for the first time.
302202.name: Dating Game?

302203.desc: The blunt approach is not my style, but I cannot have Noshiro think I only inch my way to success... Oh, I was just talking to myself, Commander. Hehe, so anyway, would you mind being my partner for tonight's party?
302203.name: Blue Butterfly's Confession

302210.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number two – Noshiro.
302210.name: Noshiro

302211.desc: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't you?
302211.name: Uncharted Festival Grounds?

302212.desc: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.
302212.name: Xanadu's Eventide

302213.desc: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.
302213.name: Fragrance of the Eastern Snow

302214.desc: Why don't you unwind for a bit before you start reflecting on the day's happenings? I'm sure it'll be far more efficient that way.
302214.name: Cozy Enclave

302215.desc: Welcom...?! What are you doing here? Wait, don't leave—I was just surprised, that's all... Well, what would you like to order?
302215.name: Hold the Ice

302216.desc: ...Take that! Heehee... Ahaha! Phew... I know you don't like admitting defeat, but I got you pretty good there. I might have tried a bit too hard, but I'm pretty sure you were the one who told me to give it my all.
302216.name: Unwinding in the Sunshine

302218.desc: Receiving everyone's blessings is truly a deeply moving experience. But for now, let's set everything else aside and partake of our sweet bliss. After all, you're not just a spectator anymore– we're in this ride together, hehe~
302218.name: A Tale of Two Lovers

302230.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number four – Sakawa.
302230.name: Sakawa

302231.desc: Welcome! Heehee, you came because you were just so keen to see me, am I right? Then I've got to make you feel real welcome♪
302231.name: The Colors of Love

302232.desc: Wow, look how far you pursued me. You must have really, reeeally wanted to see me, huh, Commander~? Heheh, want a popsicle?
302232.name: Icy Indulgence

302233.desc: Laaa la-laaa♪ Oh, Commander. Here to see me again? I know you're madly in love and want to watch me practice, but people will think you're weird if you keep coming and going constantly. Heehee♪
302233.name: The Keys of Love

303010.desc: First ship of the {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:53}.
303010.name: Furutaka

303019.desc: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?
303019.name: Furutaka (Retrofit)

303029.desc: Performance upgraded, improvements complete. This way I can finally... *cough* Oh, it's nothing, Commander. I must simply be more strict with you in the future. Are you ready for your psychological examination?
303029.name: Kako (Retrofit)

303030.desc: First ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:55}.
303030.name: Aoba

303040.desc: Second ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:56}.
303040.name: Kinugasa

303060.desc: Tone-class heavy cruiser number two – Chikuma.
303060.name: Chikuma

303070.desc: First ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:63}.
303070.name: Myoukou

303080.desc: Second ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:64}.
303080.name: Nachi

303089.desc: Howzit? Now that my retrofit's all done, don't I look even more perfect than before? Maybe now, our ever-so-reserved Commander here will be super impressed by my new abilities~ Wh-what do you mean I've been staying up too late training with my rigging? W-we're not gonna talk about that!
303089.name: Nachi (Retrofit)

303090.desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number three - Ashigara
303090.name: Ashigara

303091.desc: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?
303091.name: Brief Intermission

303092.desc: This whole "fashion coordination" concept is still a bit hard for me to wrap my head around, so I'm glad Nachi helped me pick out a swimsuit. Now, I just need to... Hey, Commander! Open your mouth! H-huh?! But this is what Nachi told me to do... is there some sort of problem?!
303092.name: Kaleidoscopic Summer

303100.desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number four – Haguro.
303100.name: Haguro

303101.desc: Ow! That freakin' stings... Can't believe I actually slipped on the stairs and hit my foot. Just how clumsy am I? ...Oh, Commander? Uh, welcome?
303101.name: A Blessing in Disguise?

303102.desc: H-hey, help me out! ...No, I didn't come in here for fun. When I finished my security duty last night, I got to thinking about how I was going to give you chocolate for Valentine's and fell asleep. When I woke up, I was stuffed in this thing...
303102.name: Caught By Nightfall

303110.desc: First ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:66}.
303110.name: Takao

303112.desc: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?
303112.name: Beach Rhapsody

303113.desc: Practicing writing is a type of training, isn't it? Commander... do you want to sit down and write with me?
303113.name: The Lessons of Spring

303114.desc: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?
303114.name: School Romanza

303115.desc: Ugh... S-such shameless attire... If not for Atago saying that it would benefit me to experience different things...! It looks good on me?! I, I see...
303115.name: Full Throttle Charmer

303116.desc: My five senses are sharper than ever, perhaps even TOO sharp. No matter what trap awaits, my only way forward is to pierce through and focus on overcoming this trial... Haaah!
303116.name: Divine Exorcist's Blade

303118.desc: Commander, I've been undertaking countless bride training sessions in order to prepare for this day. As your bride, I won't let you down.
303118.name: Sakura Hanami

303120.desc: Second ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:67}.
303120.name: Atago

303121.desc: The warm breeze that gently wraps around your skin, and delicate footsteps across the white sand... isn’t this the essence of summer? Commander, what does summer mean to you?
303121.name: Summer March

303122.desc: Oh my, it's begun to snow. Commander, should we find a nice, quiet place to enjoy the view?
303122.name: Hallmarks of Winter

303123.desc: Student handbook, textbooks... twin guns, torpedoes... and what else... Huh? Commander, I'm just packing my bags for school... is there anything I'm missing?
303123.name: School Traumerei

303124.desc: So, you want big sister to be your "fleet queen"? You got it. But you'd better give it your all out there, or else I'll be upset with you!
303124.name: Stunning Speedster

303128.desc: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~
303128.name: Lily-White Vow

303130.desc: Third ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:68}.
303130.name: Maya

303140.desc: Takao-class heavy cruiser number four – Choukai.
303140.name: Choukai

303141.desc: There, that's it for the entrance... Oh welcome, Commander! I've been cleaning, so give me a moment... I'll be right with you!
303141.name: Tidy Store, Tidy Mind

303170.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number three – Suzuya.
303170.name: Suzuya

303180.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number four – Kumano.
303180.name: Kumano

303181.desc: It's time for Kumano's sexy swimsuit debut~! Just kidding~☆ Hey Commander, just where~ are~ you~ staring~? Ahaha~♡
303181.name: Fancy Waves

303182.desc: Now it's your turn, Commander! Which one's it gonna be~? You suuuure you wanna pick this card? ...I hear you, Suzuya! Stop tellin' the Commander what the cards are!
303182.name: PJ Poker Party

303183.desc: Tadah! Get a load of my... dancer outfit! So, whaddya think? Ahaha~♡ Hey, Commander, where are those eyes wandering? Did ya see something ya like?
303183.name: One Thousand and One Nights' Wishes

303191.desc: Commander~ Come over here~♥ Heehee, you look surprised... I don't think I'm dressed strangely at all. Or... is this swimsuit not enough to satisfy you, Commander?
303191.name: Sojourn Through Clear Seas

304010.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number one – Kongou.
304010.name: Kongou

304011.desc: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?
304011.name: The Beauties of Nature

304012.desc: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?
304012.name: Hospital Talent

304013.desc: It would be a shame to pass on this lovely weather, Commander. Why have a dull commute by train when you can enjoy a leisurely bicycle ride in the sunlight, hm? Heehee♪
304013.name: Breezy Commute

304020.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.
304020.name: Hiei

304021.desc: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?
304021.name: Moonlit Cruise

304022.desc: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?
304022.name: Fragrant Red Plum

304023.desc: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~
304023.name: Beauty of the White Sands

304030.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Haruna.
304030.name: Haruna

304031.desc: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.
304031.name: Free Time Before Class

304032.desc: I guess that looks right... Since Kongou chose this for me, I must trust her judgment... Um, C-Commander, would you mind helping me out? ...It's a bit hard to walk in this outfit...
304032.name: Scarlet Innocence

304033.desc: "My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking?" ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?
304033.name: The Elegant Lotus

304040.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Kirishima.
304040.name: Kirishima

304041.desc: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?
304041.name: After-School Cannon Time

304042.desc: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?
304042.name: Summery Audacity

304043.desc: "Commander, bad luck for you, but you're just going to become another notch on my blade." Haha, just kidding, it's a joke! So, what do you think? My New Year's attire is pretty snazzy, isn't it?
304043.name: Casual Dazzle

304044.desc: The Lunar New Year is known for its hustle and bustle, but it's nice to just sit down with a brush and take in the smell of ink. Hey Commander, got any words you want to see rendered in calligraphy?
304044.name: Graceful Ink Incense

304050.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi
304050.name: Amagi

304051.desc: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.
304051.name: Wending Waters, Serene Lotus

304052.desc: *munch*... Ah. Commander, the banquet isn't over yet. What brings you here? When a host sneaks out, that causes trouble for the person cleaning up after them... Heehee, I didn't say NOT to, now, did I?
304052.name: Red Kite Respite

304060.desc: Fast Battleship, second ship of the Kongou-class Hiei.
304060.name: Hiei-chan

304070.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi
304070.name: Amagi-chan

305011.desc: {namecode:79} said always dressing like a witch can be a bit old-fashioned, so she gave me a new outfit. That kid... Do you think it looks good on me, Commander?
305011.name: The Celebration of Spring

305012.desc: Changing into leisure clothes, and waiting for the return of my beloved... Milord, I too have changed since meeting you.
305012.name: Perfect Partner?

305019.desc: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and {namecode:79} to meet you.
305019.name: Fusou (Retrofit)

305021.desc: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...
305021.name: Summer Offensive?

305022.desc: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!
305022.name: Holiday Offensive

305023.desc: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?
305023.name: Dressy Black Cat

305024.desc: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!
305024.name: Sales Clerk Offensive?!

305025.desc: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?
305025.name: Vacation Offensive!

305026.desc: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!
305026.name: Street Corner Offensive!

305028.desc: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think, what do you think? Milord, do you like Yamashiro's dress~?
305028.name: Bridal Attack!

305029.desc: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!
305029.name: Yamashiro (Retrofit)

305039.desc: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!
305039.name: Ise (Retrofit)

305049.desc: Aviation battleship Hyuuga, sporting new powers, reporting in! Rest easy, Commander, I'll show you my true post-retrofit power!
305049.name: Hyuuga (Retrofit)

305051.desc: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?
305051.name: Great Fox's Respite

305052.desc: Perfect, you have arrived. As long as you are here, the usual moon-watching will prove to be much more enjoyable... Why don't you stay here today and rest for a while?
305052.name: Guardian Fox's Shining Furisode

305053.desc: I heard that it is custom to play a "sport" at this kind of event, involving throwing pillows at others. Heheh, then I shall put the might of the Big Seven on display!
305053.name: Guardian Fox's Vacation

305054.desc: Though this is a splendorous dress befitting the occasion, it is too different from my usual attire... Mutsu and Mikasa have nothing but praise for it? If you say so, then perhaps... I can take your word. Hehe.
305054.name: Guardian Fox's Procession

305058.desc: It may be presumptuous of me, but please take care of me from now on... Is that acceptable? S-Somehow, it feels a little embarrassing... Ahaha...
305058.name: Great Fox's White Gown

305061.desc: Commander, check it out! "Nothing can stop me!" Urakaze made it for me! Now I can play warring states with her! Heheh, you should know I'm a force to be reckoned with! Can't you come play with us? Why?
305061.name: Warring States Warship

305062.desc: Hmh? If fah foo, Fummamuh? ...*gulp*. I'm not lazing around! I'm just checking on the pastries that just came in! What are you doing here anyway? To "taste-test?" Or is there something wrong with the pastries? Why?
305062.name: A Maid's Mis-service?
