305081.desc: An inspection? ...You're awfully gung-ho about your work considering how hot it is outside... Surely you wouldn't have some sort of ulterior motive?
305081.name: Hometown Zest

305101.desc: "Welcome back, Master." Rather, that's what all the children at the café were saying to you when they greeted you at the door. Hehe, is this some new custom?
305101.name: Violet Moonglow

305111.desc: I found quite the nostalgic outfit when I was cleaning my wardrobe. Let's see... "Prepare to come with me on a new journey!" How do I look, Commander?
305111.name: Style of the Sakura Capital

305112.desc: It's about time for the flowers to bloom once more. Alas, how the time flies by... Ahem, Commander, let's see, would you like to go blossom-viewing with me?
305112.name: Blossom-Viewing Season

305113.desc: Even I like to dress down and unwind from time to time. Oh? This is new and exciting for you? Well, you are welcome to come see more of it from now on! Hahaha!
305113.name: Reverence for Rest and Relaxation

305114.desc: Welcome to the Sakura Empire's pop-up café... Oh, Commander! Everyone's waiting for you. Now get your butt in here and experience the full extent of our fleet's hospitality! Don't be nervous, now! Hahaha!
305114.name: A Romantic Respite

305115.desc: I was worried when you said you wanted to go on a trip with me, but... I do like getting to go sight-seeing and try on new threads. Commander, let's enjoy this to the fullest! Hahaha!
305115.name: Beauty in Indigo

305118.desc: I, battleship Mikasa, from now until eternity, pledge to you my undying love and devotion. May we help each other, encourage each other, and walk side-by-side on the same path. I hope to meet your expectations, as unworthy as I may be.
305118.name: Untarnished Splendor

305121.desc: Refreshing drinks, delicious food, warm sunshine... and a pool to beat the heat? Heh, isn't this the essence of summer?
305121.name: Poolside Persuasion

305131.desc: I love hammocks and water beds 'cause they make you feel like you're floating on waves. It's the most relaxing thing ever~♪ You oughta hop on and try for yourself, Commander~
305131.name: Shimmering Forsythia

305140.desc: Battleship Suruga, reporting for duty. It would seem that some threads of fate connect me to this port... No, don't mind my rambling. Please disregard that.
305140.name: Suruga

305141.desc: Good morning, Commander. Everyone else seems to be dressed up on this day of celebration, so this shouldn't be a problem, right?
305141.name: Hundred Flowers' Auspice

305142.desc: Oh. Fancy meeting you here... Walk to school together? Uh, sure! I know the way, so please just follow me.
305142.name: Straightfaced Model Student

305143.desc: This should do it. With how unremarkable my present is, I doubt it'll make any waves when the... Ack! Commander?! Why are you here?!
305143.name: Uneventful Holiday Greetings

306010.desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number one – Hiyou.
306010.name: Hiyou

306020.desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number two – Junyou.
306020.name: Junyou

306031.desc: While everyone slips into sweet dreams from the night's festivities, the sound of gossamer sliding off of smooth skin reaches your ears... Hehe, would you like to spend this night under the stars with me, Master~?
306031.name: The Dream of the Autumn Pillow

306050.desc: First ship of the {namecode:87}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:87}.
306050.name: {namecode:87}

306051.desc: Waaaah! My candy! Candy is spillin’ everywhere! ...Wh-why are y’all chasin’ me? Commander, help me catch the pumpkin!
306051.name: Patrolling Witch

306059.desc: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~
306059.name: Shouhou (Retrofit)

306061.desc: *yawn*... Finally, a good night's rest... Now, to pick up where I left off on that RPG... M-m-m-milord, why are you here?! I wasn't slacking off or anything, I w-w-was just... Ughh....
306061.name: Slacking Samurai

306062.desc: All right! Steady! Steadyyy! Gottem! Hahahah! Now I'll– M-Milord?! I-I'm just, umm... enjoying an after-school break!
306062.name: Dragon Hunter: Ryuujou's Rise

306071.desc: Commander, everyone seems to be busy with end-of-year preparations. If there is anything I can do to help, please let me know.
306071.name: Firebird's New Year Dance

306081.desc: An order of coconut milk... and grilled sausage. Mm, that should do it. ...Hm? Commander? Are you here to place an order, or to get away from the heat?
306081.name: Summer Shine

306082.desc: I had this outfit custom-made just for today... Do you like it, Commander? Um, that's good then... (*whispers*) Booyah.
306082.name: Mosaic of Blending Colors

306091.desc: Hehe~ If you don't have any other plans, then your only task... is to enjoy a holiday by the sea! Commander, have you switched into vacation mode yet?
306091.name: Shimmering Surf

307011.desc: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you." Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*
307011.name: Paradise Amaryllis

307012.desc: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...
307012.name: Plum and Snow

307013.desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡
307013.name: Ruby-Laced Beauty

307014.desc: This banquet is my present to you... and your attendance is the greatest reward I could hope for~ Indeed, I shall not grant you leave tonight until you pass out. Ehehe... Ahahaha~♡
307014.name: Dawn-Phoenix's Summons

307015.desc: Commander, open up. Say ahh... Heehee, heheheheh... You're like a little baby♪ Receiving a lovely new outfit and seeing a different side of you... How blessed am I?
307015.name: Precipice of Sweetness

307018.desc: We should send out even more invites... This is the best way to rid ourselves of those pesky vixens all at once!
307018.name: Deep Crimson Poppy

307021.desc: "You only live once?" Where have I heard that saying before... Commander, are you getting excited?
307021.name: Everlasting Killing Stone

307022.desc: One must wear appropriate attire for the New Year. What do you think, Commander? Let me hear your opinion.
307022.name: White Fox's New Year

307023.desc: This statue seems to have been inspired by the teachings of the Iris Orthodoxy. Though I am unfamiliar with this kind of art, gazing upon such majesty... fills one with a sense of piety. Commander, can you feel it as well?
307023.name: Exalted White Wings

307024.desc: I never thought you'd end up taking such a long trip with me just to pick up a dress... Though I'm worried about leaving my sister behind at port, I suppose I should take your advice and relax a bit.
307024.name: Gentle Blossom's Sigh

307025.desc: What are you doing up here?! Oh, it's you. I thought you went to see my sister? ...You needed a breath of fresh air? That's all fine, but you should return to my sister soon before she does something mad.
307025.name: Dusk-Simurgh's Vigil

307026.desc: I came in expecting to play an assassin, but instead I'm a dancer. Did Akashi come up with this setting? Well, whatever... As long as I get to fight, there's nothing worth complaining about. Commander, hide behind me if you ever encounter a monster.
307026.name: Snowsilk Fox Dance

307028.desc: "To hold one's hand and grow old together with him"... If it is to be with you, then it won't so bad.
307028.name: Sacred Blue Lily

307031.desc: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?
307031.name: The Crane Amidst the Pines

307032.desc: Counselor girl {namecode:93}! Remedy the school atmosphere and correct your learning attitude, and...well, in short, I protect the discipline of the school.
307032.name: The Counselor Girl

307039.desc: If I can become stronger through this... Commander, what are you staring at? Don't you still have work to do?
307039.name: Souryuu (Retrofit)

307041.desc: Without girl bullies, there would be no disciplinary girl. So...before sister catches me, let’s cause some mischief at school.
307041.name: After School Bullies

307049.desc: Retrofit complete! Aircraft Carrier Hiryuu, reporting for duty! Hahaha! I finally got the chance to use that line! I'll be counting on you once more!
307049.name: Hiryuu (Retrofit)

307050.desc: First ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:95}.
307050.name: Shoukaku

307051.desc: I prepared this outfit just for the occasion, so... Commander, you're not going to disappoint me, are you? Hehe~♪
307051.name: The Crane that Dances With the Wind

307052.desc: Hehe, this kind of work is a simple matter for me. Commander, please look forward to my performance~
307052.name: Sororal Wings

307060.desc: Second ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:96}.
307060.name: Zuikaku

307061.desc: New Elite 1st CarDiv, Zuikaku, reporting for duty! Ahh, I've always wanted to give such a cool introduction! Shoukaku would definitely make fun of me if she heard it, but I wanted to try it while everyone is in a festive mood... Commander, what'd you think?
307061.name: Ceremonial Crane

307062.desc: Commander, I volunteered to take this job in order to help you out, but this outfit... did it always require such a high degree of exposure...?
307062.name: The Wind's True Name

307071.desc: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡
307071.name: Forbidden Fruit

307072.desc: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you♡
307072.name: Phoenix's Spring Song

307073.desc: Do I make a nice race queen, my Commander...? Hehe. With these proportions, and my fantastic outfit~♡ The others couldn't hope to compare with me!
307073.name: Enraptured Companion

307074.desc: Ehehe~ There is no greater bliss than being with you after classes are over, my Commander~ The kitty here seems to agree♡
307074.name: Sweet Time After School

307075.desc: A beach date, just me and my Commander... I could walk by your side forever—No, I can't be satisfied by this alone. And neither can you... Right, my Commander?♥
307075.name: Seaside Daydreams

307078.desc: My Commander~ Do you like the location that I've chosen~? We have the entire evening to ourselves, free from the disturbance of anyone else...! Ahhh, my heart is throbbing even more vigorously than the ocean's waves~♡
307078.name: Temptation on the Sea Breeze

307081.desc: The moonlight dims beneath hazy clouds, and the lights of the night sky begin to shine... The moon, and this sake, are both intoxicating... Will you not enjoy this fine evening with me...?
307081.name: Dreams of the Hazy Moon

307082.desc: Hnnh... Such clamors of merriment... Would this one be welcome amidst these festivities? Alas... If you so desire, how can this one refuse...?
307082.name: Moonlit Chrome

307083.desc: This world of pristine sand that you have envisioned, a mirage that fits only within the confines of a dream and a reverie... No matter how many times we meet here, this one finds herself drawn to this place again and again...
307083.name: Dreamy White Sands

307100.desc: With the magicks of the Sakura Empire, changing my form like this is a trifle... Hehehe, Commander? Does this Akagi please you?
307100.name: Akagi μ

307110.desc: With these clothes, and upon this stage... Ahaha... Ahahaha... Fate has ordained that my Commander shall fall for me here... Commander, please listen to the song of my love until the very end~♡
307110.name: Taihou μ

307121.desc: It's– summer– festival– time–!! Uhh, well, maybe it's a bit too late for a "summer" festival, so maybe a regular festival is fine? Well, the important thing is that you have lots of fun, Commander! Because I sure as heck will!
307121.name: Night-Illuminating Festival

307122.desc: Mmmh~ When it gets real hot, whether you're a shipgirl or an ordinary person, the place to go to cool down is always either the mountains or the beach, right? But what if I told you, that when you're at a rooftop pool, you not only get the great views of climbing up a mountain, but also the refreshing coolness of splashing around in the water? Am I right or am I right, Commander? ...Heeeey, are you even listening?!
307122.name: Shallow-Water Leisure

308011.desc: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?
308011.name: Departure's Gentle Breeze

308012.desc: So sleepy... Hey, Commandeeer? Do you wanna nap with me and my torpedo?
308012.name: Pillowy Paradise

308013.desc: I thought I'd try on this bunny costume! Hehehe, do you like it? If you think it's cute, I wanna hear you say it~
308013.name: Blossoming Bunny

308021.desc: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!
308021.name: Deep-Sea Rabbit

308022.desc: Commander, are you also waiting for the fireworks to start? There's still some time, so let's have a little chat!
308022.name: Shortly Before the Fireworks

308041.desc: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?
308041.name: Coral Reef Bunny

308042.desc: Commander, Happy Lunar New Year. Would you like some sweet wine to celebrate? Oh, be careful not to drink too much~
308042.name: Sweet Wine of Celebration

308050.desc: Type B3 Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-56.
308050.name: I-56

308051.desc: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...
308051.name: Wallflower in the Corner

308061.desc: I look different from usual? That's obvious, isn't it... All right, all right, I was just giving you a hard time. We're at a festival, so we might as well enjoy ourselves!
308061.name: Festive Mood!

312010.desc:
Repair ship {namecode:98}
<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking</color>
312010.name: Akashi

312011.desc: Commander, how does Akashi's new outfit look, nya? Isn't it cute? If you like it, then put a ring on it. I mean, everyone's gone out to play... if you don't help empty my inventory, I'll go broke, nya!
312011.name: Akashi's in the Red, Nya!

312012.desc: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?
312012.name: The Black Cat Cometh!

312013.desc: Ohh, it's Commander, nya. Have you come to buy Akashi's new work, nya? Today's a holiday, so go ahead and enjoy yourself, nya~
312013.name: Welcome to AzurCon!

312014.desc: Hehehe, come on in, nya! Can I help you find something, nya? Your genial and knowledgeable staff, Akashi, will gladly provide her detailed recommendations, nya!
312014.name: Welcome to Sofmap!

312018.desc: Commander, because of your continued patronage of my shop, I have no choice but to return the favor with my body, nya~! ...Just kidding, nya. Having that said, I really do love you, Commander. Even more than I love gems, nya~
312018.name: White Cat's Repayment

317010.desc: Type A Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-13.
317010.name: I-13

319011.desc: Ack... Owww... My apologies, Commander, I seem to have slipped on something... At times, it's hard to notice things I'm about to step on... Ugh...
319011.name: Hot Springs Relaxation

319012.desc: Hyah?! U-Umm, I can't get out... Oh, Commander?! I'm sorry! I tripped while I was cleaning, and I ended up stuck in here! Umm... What do I do now...
319012.name: Maid for Mayhem

319013.desc: ♪~ Commander, how'd that sound? Hmm... I just started learning last minute, so I guess things aren't coming together after all... But, why do I sound off-pitch even though I'm playing everything exactly the way I was taught...?
319013.name: Robust Floral Strings

331050.desc: Commander, Happy New Year's. In this coming year, please continue to look after me...
331050.name: Pulse of the New Year

331051.desc: Commander, thank you for coming to the party. Ayanami... has been waiting for you. ...I look a bit scary? I'm not sure I get it... I guess.
331051.name: Nightfall Raiment

331052.desc: No, Ryuujou! Samurai builds should stay back during the boss! ...Oh, welcome, Commander. I'm busy with this game right now, so just make yourself at home or something.
331052.name: Off-Duty Battle Station Gear

331054.desc: Welcome. Ayanami will be taking your order, yes. Will this be dine-in, or to-go? I would personally recommend the cola.
331054.name: Cola Fills You With Determination

331055.desc: Ultimate Ability: Dynamic Kick! ...Oh, I used my skill on the wrong target. Sorry, can we try that again?
331055.name: Dynamic Kick!

331056.desc: *fidget, fidget*... Oh, how's the party? Yes, I get a little angsty when I'm without a weapon... I envy your ability to stay calm no matter what.
331056.name: Disarming Deep Blue

399011.desc: Milord, it's starting to snow... If it suits you, please take shelter under Ibuki's umbrella.
399011.name: Winter Sylph's Reverie

399012.desc: This is my first time wearing Western clothes... Um, Milord! Does this outfit... suit Ibuki well...?
399012.name: Snow on the Wind

399013.desc: The Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" is... filled with fun, liveliness, and pure jubilation. I can feel my true feelings welling up... Maybe, an environment like this would suit me pretty well...
399013.name: Arrival of Spring

399014.desc: I'm glad you've returned, Milord. I've changed my attire in order to better carry out your order–for us to "relax together." Now then... could you please instruct me on how to proceed?
399014.name: Tranquil Sunya

399021.desc: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!
399021.name: Izumo's Thousand Cherry Trees

399031.desc: All the preparations are now complete... Commander, let us sally forth and conquer these festival grounds! ...But before that, can we get something to eat first?
399031.name: Celebration Conquest!

399033.desc: Mm, preparations complete. If I keep it up, the production will surely be a great success. The doves have been on their best behavior too. Commander, what do you think about Kitakaze's magic show?
399033.name: Night of Doves and Magic

399041.desc: Commander? Oh, I haven't quite finished changing. My hair still needs work... Sorry, would you mind waiting a bit longer?
399041.name: Soft Voice of Spring

399048.desc: I must be dreaming, to be able to don this white veil... Haha, though, what's more important is our life together afterwards! Commander, please look forward to the rich fruit of my bridal training~
399048.name: Lily-White Longing

399051.desc: All righty, one freshly-sliced plate of sashimi coming right up! ...Huh? I'm coming across too aggressive? Even after I went through all this trouble for you, you still have something to nitpick about? ...Well, whatever. Enjoy your meal!
399051.name: Slice, Dice, and Serve

399052.desc: Katana... at the ready. Hmph, you again? Never expected you to know anything about music, the way you've been out there conquering the waves with us this whole time. Come then, let me test how good your tastes are with this song!
399052.name: Flash of Silk and Strings

399061.desc: You couldn't have picked a better time to come. Allow me to treat you to a cup of the Dragon God's benevolence– Uhh, I'll go boil some water right now, so sit tight. After you finish the tea, shall we kick back and relax awhile?
399061.name: The Comfy Dragon God

401011.desc: Because she’s the Z1, her results will of course be NO.1! Hehe, no matter where she goes, Z1-sama will always be the best!
401011.name: "Rebellious" Top Student

401019.desc: Hmm... So this is a retrofit, huh? Not bad! Rejoice once more, Commander, for no task or enemy is too daunting for the new and improved Z1!
401019.name: Z1 (Retrofit)

401021.desc: Commander, I do wonder if your order to "come dressed in new clothes" was simply your way of saying "I want to see you in a casual outfit." No matter the case, I'm happy to oblige.
401021.name: High-Rise, High-Style

401022.desc: Being able to see you all flabbergasted makes changing into this outfit worth it. Are you going to keep standing there like a scarecrow? Come over here~ Who knows, we might even be able to see the fireworks from this spot.
401022.name: Of Koi and Evening Hues

401161.desc: Heh heh! Count your lucky stars, Commander, because you're just in time – to witness the one-and-only Z16 knock this thing right outta the ballpark!
401161.name: Guaranteed Grand Slam!

401231.desc: This is going to be on the exam! If you don't take thorough notes, I am going to punish you!
401231.name: Philosophy Sensei

401232.desc: Haiyaaah! It's up to you, Ayanami! Oh, Commander! Are you actually keeping score? We might not be having a serious match, but that's no excuse for you to stand around and do nothing.
401232.name: Breezy Doubles

401233.desc: Welcome! A table for one today? Um... Commander, my smile doesn’t look stiff... right?
401233.name: Perfect Smile?

401234.desc: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?
401234.name: The Banquet's Honor Student

401235.desc: Hi, welcome! How may I serve y– It's you, Commander?! Err, well, I'm working as a trainee at this Sakura Empire-style café, you see... What do you think of this outfit?
401235.name: Café Trainee @New Base

401236.desc: Jeez... Javelin's got what it takes, but I'm really concerned about Laffey and Ayanami. Oh well, I guess it's up to me to manage them... Commander, please don't forget to support me too.
401236.name: Serious Idol @Acting Manager?!

401237.desc: Commander, please help hold onto the ladder. I've almost got the book... Just a little more... All right... C-Commander?! Please don't look up!
401237.name: The Eyecatch in the Rye?

401238.desc: Whew... Sorry to keep you waiting. I was having a hard time deciding which outfit to wear... Ah, um... how do I look?
401238.name: Schwarze Hochzeit

401239.desc: My efficiency should be upgraded along with my performance. Paperwork, battle plans... I can handle them all! Commander, be prepared, we’ll be very busy~
401239.name: Z23 (Retrofit)

401241.desc: Come, human! The rite of festivities is upon us! Come hither, and let us revel in this foreign holiday together!
401241.name: Festival-going Fiend

401242.desc: Heh heh... As expected, you couldn't even last for a second! Winning too easily takes all the fun out of it... You, the mortal over there, I'll give you the honor of being my next opponent!
401242.name: The Devil on the Court

401243.desc: "Sing your praises to the Fiend of Crimson Darkness, Z24!" ... Hmm, maybe I should go with "Bow down in astonishment!"... Ah, yes! Mortal, you've come at a most opportune time! Hurry and tell me what you think of my new catchphrase! ...Actually, get me down from here first!
401243.name: Blood-Red Dance Beneath the Moon

401251.desc: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?
401251.name: Hot Summer's Cool Breeze

401261.desc: Commander, welcome to my pad! Ah, give me a sec, let me go grab all the snacks and drinks and games!
401261.name: Sharing is Caring

401281.desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Is there anything you'd like to do on New Year's Day? Say, why don't we try doing all of that stuff, all at once~?
401281.name: New Year Smorgasbord!

401282.desc: Prosit, Commander! I think these wild animals were attracted by the champagne's aroma. But they're well-behaved and like being petted. Do you want to be petted too, Commander?
401282.name: Sylvan Celebration

401351.desc: Commander, and all my fellow friends of the fleet, Happy New Year's! This time, your favorite idol Z35 will be presenting a brand new Sakura-themed collaboration, "Projekt Kirschblüte!" Everyone, thank you for your continued support!
401351.name: Projekt Kirschblüte

401352.desc: "Welcome, my beloved Master♡ Heehee, I've been waiting here for you for sooo long!" Heheh, did you get good pics this time? My beloved Master♪
401352.name: Liebender Engel

401461.desc: The bustling beach, clamoring with waves of joyfulness... experiencing this kind of summer is a first for me, but I don't dislike it...
401461.name: Her First Summer

401462.desc: Through the sweat and tears, striving for your goals. Rejoice in victory, sink within defeat... How fascinating, this "sports meet" may be.
401462.name: Girls' Relay

401463.desc: Dancing beams of light, shimmering on-stage; uplifted voices, joined as one by song... Upon this unknown stage, my heart doth flutter... Yet this sensation, is quite refreshing.
401463.name: Star-Lit★Chocolate

401464.desc: "Jianzhi," the art of breathing life into works of cut paper... is a world beyond my imagination. If these decorations are said to usher in blessings... are they akin to a coat-of-arms or a holy seal?
401464.name: Jianzhi Fantasia

401465.desc: Cast your eyes upon this bit of dust. As I was entrusted with the cleaning, I shall not allow this dust to remain. Will you also join me in this battle?
401465.name: Chronicles of the Dust Wars

401991.desc: Hmph! You really think this brainless trap can keep me entangled forever? I don't need your help! I can break free by myself! ...Umm, what the hell? Why can't I do it?!
401991.name: Hunter Becomes Hunted

402039.desc: Hmm... I feel like I can work even more efficiently than before. Commander, please rest assured, I will never betray your expectations.
402039.name: Köln (Retrofit)

402040.desc:
Leipzig-class light cruiser, Leipzig.
<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking</color>
402040.name: Leipzig

402041.desc: Commander, ah, um... We have all new items on the menu, and they're on sale for a limited time only... P-please give them a try! Phew... Th-thank goodness, I managed to not flub it...
402041.name: Storefront Training

402049.desc: I feel like Fishy is a lot more capable than before, but I don't feel much different... M-maybe Fishy was the one to get a retrofit instead of me?!
402049.name: Leipzig (Retrofit)

402051.desc: Since you so readily accepted my invitation to go on a vacation together, you must be planning to... Ahh, what I meant is, we can leave at any time if you're ready...!
402051.name: Spring Wanderer

402061.desc: You little...! Look what a damn mess you made! And I'm the one who's gotta clean it up now! ...Oh. Perfect timing, Commander. Could use a hand with the floor here, after what this little turd did.
402061.name: Cat Café Cleanup

402062.desc: Here's an idea – how 'bout putting down the camera and actually enjoyin' the open sea? I'll move the swim ring so you can chill in the breeze with me!
402062.name: Gone Fishing

402071.desc: Raise your head, my darling human. O lost soul, you have three options – become Emden's meal, become Emden's prisoner... "Or become Emden's vassal. Our vassal♥"
402071.name: White-Black Partita

402072.desc: Welcome, my darling human. Are you looking for something? If it is Emden you seek, you have already found her. "We, Emden, are before your very eyes."
402072.name: Moonsilver Union

402081.desc: As the mistress of this manor, I c-command thee to kneel... No, of course. I mean, what authority do I have to issue commands? I'm better suited to be a maid than a mistress...
402081.name: The Throne of Misfortune

402082.desc: Are you also having trouble sleeping, Commander? I-I thought so... It must be because I was praying for you to have sweet dreams... Look what I've done – now, neither of us can fall asleep... Urgh...
402082.name: Sleepless Night's Wishes

402083.desc: G-good day, Commander. I'm ready to be your model... Ugh, there's probably going to be an accident if I wish that you'll take cute photos... Better clear my head just to be sure.
402083.name: Beauty Beneath the Spring Limelight

402101.desc: Wanted to feast your eyes on this, didn't you? Haha, there's no point trying to deny it. All your petty desires are clear as day to me, so why not just be honest about it?
402101.name: Dark Dragon, Brilliant Beach

403010.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Admiral Hipper
403010.name: Admiral Hipper

403012.desc: W-well? Does this kimono look good on me? ...R-really? Duh, I know it looks GREAT on me! Who really cares what you think... C-can't be me... No, I didn't say anything!
403012.name: Sunshine by the Hot Spring

403021.desc: Heheheh☆ You're lagging behind, Commander! Pick up the pace or you'll be left behind! Just kidding~ I'll slow down for you so we can stick together!
403021.name: High-Altitude Head Over Heels

403030.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Prinz Eugen
403030.name: Prinz Eugen

403031.desc: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?
403031.name: Unfading Smile

403032.desc: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?
403032.name: Profusion of Flowers

403033.desc: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...
403033.name: Cordial Cornflower

403034.desc: Viel Glück~ Are you having a good time, Commander? Just know that the only person I'm cheering for... is you~
403034.name: Final Lap

403035.desc: Guten Abend~ So, what do you think? Pretty great view, right? Hehe, I was talking about the night scenery outside, you know~?
403035.name: Kindred Evening Spirits

403038.desc: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~
403038.name: Symphonic Fate

403041.desc: For a servant, your eyes are good... *coughs*... I'm an Ironblood Princess, the Queen of Night, Deutschland! Servant? No. I am the first of my family. Come, kiss the ring of royalty!
403041.name: Dark Demon Princess

403042.desc: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~
403042.name: Service Time?!

403043.desc: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!
403043.name: Demon Princess' Dark Hour Banquet

403044.desc: Why are so many people out and about during a holiday? ...That's it! Lowly animal, was it your idea to prepare all this to surprise me...?! Heh... Hehe, that's right, don't you dare disappoint me!
403044.name: Lantern-Lit Ruler

403050.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser number three – Admiral Graf Spee.
403050.name: Admiral Graf Spee

403051.desc: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?
403051.name: Girl's Sunday

403052.desc: I never dreamt that I'd be able to don this outfit and live a normal, peaceful life... Thank you, Commander...
403052.name: Peaceful Daily Life

403053.desc: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!
403053.name: A Novel Anniversary

403054.desc: My sister just wouldn't stop bugging me, so I finally caved and agreed to do this... Anyways, all I have to do is get up on stage and sing, right?
403054.name: World's♥Cutest

403070.desc: Huh? Why are you staring at me like I'm some weirdo? I'll have you know, it's not like I wanted to do this or anything!
403070.name: Admiral Hipper μ

403080.desc: Heavy cruiser Roon, reporting for idol activities and associated experimental equipment testing. Today, we fight not with fire and sword, but with the power of song.
403080.name: Roon μ

403091.desc: Phew... Changing into these clothes took quite a long time~ So, how does it look? A fine mixing of different cultures, wouldn't you agree? Ahaha, Happy New Year, Commander!
403091.name: Fireworks and Tapestries

403092.desc: *ptwee*! Remember: safety first! Commander, you've got to do your stretches before going in the pool! Be thorough, or I'll get mad at you!
403092.name: Rabbit on Watch

403093.desc: Listen up, Commander! I'm the one in charge of this school's seedy underbelly here at this port, so you'd better do what I tell you to! In return, I'll offer you my protection! Ahaha~♪
403093.name: Secret Boss o' the Underworld?

403094.desc: Alrighty, I'm gonna sing a song for you now! Surprised by how jazzy and womanly I can be, are you? Ahahah!
403094.name: Heinrich on Stage

403101.desc: Zzz... Huh? Did I doze off? I just meant to rest my eyes for a sec after closing up, but look how long I slept... Hang on, why are you still here, Commander?
403101.name: After-Hours Service

403111.desc: "Foolish, pitiable creature. Kneel before your Goddess!" Heehee! Hahahah, ahahahaha♥ You're the Commander, silly. You don't need to play along unless you want to.
403111.name: Breaker under the Blood Moon

403120.desc: Admiral Hipper-class heavy cruiser – Prinz Eugen.
403120.name: Little Prinz Eugen

403130.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser – Admiral Graf Spee.
403130.name: Little Spee

404011.desc: A festival, huh? Going for days without fighting is boring, not to mention not my style. C'mon, Commander, isn't there *something* exciting I can do during this "Lunar New Year" festival?
404011.name: Panther und Pflaume

404021.desc: These Halloween festivities are quite interesting, in a good way. Getting dressed up in these costumes isn't such a bad experience either. Commander, what do you think of my costume?
404021.name: Nightmarish Succubus

404031.desc: There it is – Dracula's Castle, brought into this world by chaos itself... On my honor, I swear I will put an end to the divine bloodline!
404031.name: Heir of the Vampire Killer

404032.desc: How do I look, Commandant? I thought you may like seeing me in a dress, however I don't know if this is what you desired or not...
404032.name: Floral Liberation

404041.desc: "Have you come to accept your fate, human? Heehee~" ...Don't just stand there, Commander. Say something!
404041.name: Everlasting Blood Banquet

404042.desc: Om, nom... Hmm. Hey! This is pretty good! I mean, of course it's good – it's Empery cuisine! Commander, open wide and I'll give you a dumpling alley oop. Say "aah"!
404042.name: Steaming-Hot Treat

404048.desc: *yawn*, finally, I get to lie down. Tell you what, I'm gonna have a nap... Hm? The ceremony's still not over? Hrmh... Look, it's not important. You should just come lie next to me, Commander!
404048.name: Sleeping White Beauty

404051.desc: Hah! This donut now belongs to Brünhilde! Alright, now for the finish line... C-Commander? Sorry, but there's no time for chit-chat... I'll be going now!
404051.name: Grain-Seizing Grani

405011.desc: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...
405011.name: Beacon of the Iron Blood

405012.desc: Welcome, what would you like to order? ...If you want, we can drop this charade. I'm not used to being a waiter anyway, so I prefer it this way. Hehe.
405012.name: Iron-Black Elysium

405021.desc: Summer... In the past, it was always just a hot and stifling season... But now...? Doesn't my outfit tell the whole story? Let's get going, there's bound to be a lot of people on the beach.
405021.name: Snow-Melting Summer

405022.desc: I bet Bismarck must've been thinking about how to invite me to the party, but ended up asking you to do it, Commander. Hehe... Let's get going soon. It's best not to keep her waiting.
405022.name: Iron Blood Snowstorm

405023.desc: They have a peculiar way of wishing a happy New Year in the Sakura Empire. In line with their traditions, I've put on this new outfit. I hope it doesn't... look strange on me. ...You like it? I see... That being the case, I'll keep wearing it for the time
405023.name: Seasonal Pine and the Frost Flower

405024.desc: It's all right, I just got here myself. I will say, it's strangely reassuring to know I'm not the only one nervous on this day.
405024.name: A Vase for the Frost Flower

405031.desc: *sigh* Do you really have to bother me during my break? ...It's a joke, no need to take it so seriously. I was looking for someone to kill some time with anyway.
405031.name: Mayhem Maid

405032.desc: That was a pretty good race – reckon you'll get first place next time, though? ...Hmh. Easier said than done. You know they won't settle for second place – and hopefully neither will you, Commander.
405032.name: Ignition Matrician

405041.desc: You, mop the floor. You, take care of the windows. Once that's done... Ah, Commander. Excuse us, we're in the middle of cleaning the area. If you have need of me, I must ask you to wait.
405041.name: Tidying in the Moonlight

405051.desc: Ah, you've already gotten changed, Commander? I'm just... Well, I need to do something about my hair before I go back in the water.
405051.name: Crystal-Clear Holiday

406011.desc: I've been waiting for you, Comander. As per my sister's recommendation, I've put on this Sakura Empire kimono. It was very tricky to get into, I might add... That aside, how do I look? ...Good enough, I hope?
406011.name: Obsidian Elegance

406012.desc: Ah, I've kept you waiting. I do apologize that it took so long to get changed into this outfit. Now, Commander, won't you come show me your chivalry and escort me down these stairs?
406012.name: Urbane Onyx

406013.desc: I've been waiting forever for this season to arrive. It's a perfect time, the waves wait for nobody, so I'm off for now. I'll make sure to teach you how to surf later, so look forward to it.
406013.name: Wave-Washed Paradise

406021.desc: Thank you all for waiting! Large mugs of Iron Blood beer, just as ord–– W-waaah?! Nnngh...! Phew, somehow managed to not spill anything... Wh-what's your deal?!
406021.name: Time to Show Off?

406022.desc: Still not here yet...? Geez, I'll give the Commander what-for for coming later than me... Huh? C-Commander? N-no, I happened to come an hour early, is all...
406022.name: Pure-Hearted Bad Girl

406031.desc: *lick*... Hmm. The fact that you can just stand there must mean that you don't mind the heat. It's okay, though. If you don't come in, I'm more than happy to have this pool all to myself~♪
406031.name: A Lick of Summer

407011.desc: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.
407011.name: Beachside Urd

407030.desc: Graf Zeppelin-class aircraft carrier – Peter Strasser.
407030.name: Peter Strasser

407031.desc: Eugen, you said that this was is a ceremonial outfit from the Sakura Empire? Surprisingly, it does seem to suit me rather well. Oh, I'm supposed to offer my well-wishes for the New Year at this time, yes?
407031.name: Chronos's Kalendae

407032.desc: You already know, don't you? Since I spent so much of my precious time changing into a dress for your sake... Heh, I'll be taking plenty of your time in return. Hehehe.
407032.name: A Moment Frozen in Pure White

407033.desc: Heheheh, it may be a new year, but don't forget to be punctual. Just as you've refurnished this study into a Dragon Empery style, I've changed clothes to match. This little book club is just for the two of us, and I mean to suit the mood.
407033.name: Lustrous Jade of the Golden House

408010.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-81.
408010.name: U-81

408011.desc: *Ugh*... I figured this bulky dress would be hard to move in... Huh? I look pretty? Aha, ahaha... You're makin' me blush...
408011.name: Soft Serenade

408012.desc: Over here, Commander! I came because you said we were going to go moon-viewing together! I even brought tea and mooncakes.
408012.name: Lantern-Lit Full Moon

408020.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-47.
408020.name: U-47

408021.desc: I haven't seen much of the world on land... Commander, want to explore it with me?
408021.name: Rookie Rider

408022.desc: Sigh... I'd much rather be in a nice, quiet place like this over the din and clamor of the venue... Wouldn't you agree, Commander? I see. Well, come sit here then.
408022.name: Eigenen Raum

408023.desc: Coming through! Steer clear! Oh, it's you, Commander. Talk to you later – I've got coffee to deliver.
408023.name: Urban Maid

408024.desc: An empty study with a cushy couch. The perfect place to relax. Whew... Go ahead and read a book if you want, Commander. If that'll be all then I'm gonna take a nap.
408024.name: Sanguine Moon Sojourn

408025.desc: Nice. I've found a legendary luck-bringing carp, like... Oh. I almost had it, too... Sorry, Commander.
408025.name: Hook, Line, and Sinker

408030.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-557.
408030.name: U-557

408040.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-556.
408040.name: U-556

408041.desc: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!
408041.name: Party Knight!

408050.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-73.
408050.name: U-73

408051.desc: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!
408051.name: Science Rules!

408052.desc: In today's chemistry lesson, we'll learn how to make a warming cup of tea and an optional concoction to enhance its flavor! Will you do the honor of taste-testing it, Commander?
408052.name: New Year's Chemistry

408060.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-101.
408060.name: U-101

408061.desc: Commander, welcome to the school band! Why'd I join the band? The reason's simple - there's no Motorbike Club at school, haha! Just kidding~! Actually, I'm quite fond of music as well, heh.
408061.name: Ironbrass Trombonist

408070.desc: Iron Blood Type IXC submarine – U-522.
408070.name: U-522

408080.desc: Raaaawr. U-110 is a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Mess with me and I'll bite yooouuu.
408080.name: U-110

408081.desc: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.
408081.name: Kleiner Hai

408082.desc: I have to wear beautiful clothes to a party, or so Bulldog said. So, I had everyone help me pick out beautiful clothes. Commander, I'm beautiful, right? Eh... cute?
408082.name: A Cute, Sharky Reverie

408083.desc: The horned idol U-110 splashes onto the staaage. I'll sing all the baddies to obliviooon. I'm scaaary. Raaawr. Raaawr♪
408083.name: Garnished Supershark

408084.desc: Commander, happy new yeeear. I'm no bunny, I'm a shaaark. Not a cute shark, but a crimson, scaaary shark. Raaawr.
408084.name: New Year, Small Shark

408085.desc: I'm gathering mushrooms, not garlic cloooves. The edible ones are gonna go in a hearty hot pot that'll warm me and my frieeends. Raaawr.
408085.name: Springtime Shark

408090.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-96.
408090.name: U-96

408091.desc: Nice timing. I just finished an intense battle. The result...? Of course I won. What? Did you want to have a match against me?
408091.name: Secret Gaming Session

408092.desc: Mmgh... Guh... Ahhh! These things are heavier than they look... Oh, there you are. You work out too, do ya? Feel free to join me if you've not just come to tease me.
408092.name: How Heavy Are Those Barbells?

408100.desc: Iron Blood Type IXA submarine – U-37.
408100.name: U-37

408101.desc: Now then, please lend your ears to this song I shall offer you... Wait, Commander, are you spacing out again? Even though I went through all this trouble to learn this song from my friends in the Sakura fleet... Please pay attention, okay? I'm starting ov
408101.name: New Year's Nightingale

408110.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-410.
408110.name: U-410

408111.desc: Happy Lunar New Year. Have you cooked up a scheme for this year's festival? Hehehe~ I'm of course talking about giving out New Year's gifts and hanging up decorations. I've devised a master plan of my own.
408111.name: Spring Festival Scheme

408112.desc: And for my finishing move... maybe something like this? Heehee. What do your eyes think, Commander?
408112.name: Practice Makes Perfect

408120.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-1206
408120.name: U-1206

408121.desc: Welcome! Oh, Hey, Commander! Heheh, so how do you like my maid getup? Looks pretty nice, if I do say so myself!
408121.name: Maid Just for You

431230.desc: *sigh*... Taking care of Meowfficers is more work than you'd think... They're awfully needy for support units. Commander, make absolute sure you don't turn out like them.
431230.name: Keeper of the Comf-Fort

431232.desc: N-no way... I lost the gear I worked so hard for because the upgrade failed, and now I'm completely out of gold... Ugh, I'm going to have to go farm the dungeon all over again...
431232.name: Upgrade Failure?!

431233.desc: Sure, I've worn black dresses in the past, but this time I decided to incorporate a bit of red and white, per Eugen's suggestion. This is sure to invite the Commander to dance wi– C-Commander?! Did you just get here? I see. Uhh... How do you like my dress?
431233.name: Tanz der Blumen

499011.desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...
499011.name: Dark Red Grin

499012.desc: It's so nice getting away from the bustling party hall and being alone with you, Commander. I'm eager to see what we'll do now as your idea of a... "break"~
499012.name: Viridescent Lullaby

499021.desc: I see, so this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire. Exquisitely crafted, comfortable to the touch, and elegantly designed... How to wear it? ...My child, what are you talking about?
499021.name: Dark Raiments of Gagaku

499028.desc: Ahh, the dreamlike beauty of this variation... let us write down this movement so that it may continue forever, my sweet child.
499028.name: Zeremonie of the Cradle

499032.desc: Ah! Changed already? Just wait a minute... No, you don't have to leave. I'm almost done.
499032.name: The Silkiest Brew

499041.desc: I thought I would never have time to pursue the fine arts, and yet here I am now. Your thoughts, Commander? Eastern as this calligraphy may be, does it not suit the connotations of my name?
499041.name: Black Strokes upon Blank Snow

499051.desc: Hmph. They think being a maid is so difficult, do they? I could do this with my eyes clo– What?! H-how long have YOU been here?!
499051.name: Iron Blood's Dragon Maid

499052.desc: New decorations, new outfits, and countless preparations to make... Lunar New Year is quite the busy time of year. Go on, see to your duties. I'm well aware how essential you are to this holiday's smooth operation. Just don't keep me waiting all day. Heehee.
499052.name: Golden Dragon Among Auspicious Clouds

499061.desc: My hair is a mess... There we go. No, I don't need a hand. I am here to serve you in this fleeting dream of yours. Enjoy it while it lasts. Hehehe.
499061.name: The Conquered Unhulde

499071.desc: Woah, so this is the Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" that I've heard so much about. But, why are they celebrating it in the middle of winter? And you, Commander – why are you helping with such a grandiose... Whuah?! What was that noise?!
499071.name: The Gate Dragon's Advent

499081.desc: My, my. I'm quite surprised you're still able to stay awake. As expected of the Commander– even a dose of Felix Schultz's special concoction isn't enough to put you under... but that ends here. It's your fault for peeping on me slacking off in the first place, so be nice and obedient and succumb to me already~♪
499081.name: Sweet, Sleepy "Revenge"

499091.desc: It's just the two of us now, Contract Binder. Come – play a game with me and immerse yourself in the pleasures this place offers. The loser of this game, of course, must accept a punishment tonight♡
499091.name: Delirious Duel

501012.desc: "Boundless is the beauty of evening's glow, but alas––" ...Oh, that doesn't have any special meaning, I've just been hanging around Hai Tien too much. (*whispers*) But, it's true... Our time together is far too short, just like the evening light...
501012.name: Setting Sun, Hearts as One

501019.desc: An Shan, retrofitting complete! With this new power, Commander, I'll protect both you and my sisters! But first... Umm, I need to double-check how these missiles work...!
501019.name: An Shan (Retrofit)

501020.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No.2 - Fu Shun (102)
501020.name: Fu Shun

501021.desc: Heh-hey! Just hooked us another baozi~! We're in for one heckuva haul today! ...Eh? Huh, Commander?! Th-this is, uhh... yeah, we're just playing a normal game... totally...
501021.name: The Unbreakable Baozi Heist

501030.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 3 - Chang Chun (103)
501030.name: Chang Chun

501031.desc: Ta-da! My pajamas are finally finished! Now to snuggle up until I'm all warm! Eh~ Ehhh? But sis, I don't want to get out! Ack, did Tai Yuan purposely make this tail big and thick to make it easier for you?
501031.name: The Joy of Spring

501032.desc: Commander, hurry up and plug your ears! Th-this isn't a joke! Um... Seriously, that big ol' doozy over there is about to blow!
501032.name: Fortune Arrives in Red

501039.desc: All done with my retrofit~ Now, time to test out my new toys... Err, I mean, time to test the firepower of my new armaments! Oh, watch your head, Commander! Wouldn't want one of the missiles to lock onto you.
501039.name: Chang Chun (Retrofit)

501040.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 4 - Tai Yuan (104)
501040.name: Tai Yuan

501041.desc: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...
501041.name: The Golden Dragon's Festivities

501049.desc: Phew... Tai Yuan, retrofit complete. Thanks for supporting me this whole time, Commander. With this new equipment, I'll be able to get one step closer to catching up to my sisters.
501049.name: Tai Yuan (Retrofit)

501050.desc: Vulcan Stettin 1,000-ton torpedo destroyer – Lung Wu.
501050.name: Lung Wu

501051.desc: Happy New Year, Commander... Having that said, the others said they had a surprise for me, but then ended up banning me from the kitchen... I didn't do anything bad, did I? I'm real worried... Can't I at least take a look at what's going on there? Ugh... How about you go check it out in my stead? P-pretty please, Commander!
501051.name: Ascendant Dragon's Spring Feast

501060.desc: Vulcan Stettin 1,000-ton torpedo destroyer – Hu Pen.
501060.name: Hu Pen

501061.desc: Let's usher in the New Year with the sound of gongs and firecrackers~! Whaddya think? Lion dances are pretty awesome, aren't they? So, Commander, who's got more oomph in their dance steps? Me, or Lung Wu? C'mon, hurry up and decide~!
501061.name: Prancing Tiger Welcomes the Spring

501071.desc: H-Happy New Year, Commander... Umm, uhh... C-could you please help me down first? ....Waah, I promise I won't have any more "adventures" in the kitchen...
501071.name: Flying Clouds, Flailing Pranks

502011.desc: I am truly honored to be able to share this wondrous scenery with you on such a festive occasion, Commander. Umm... I'm not just saying that out of courtesy. We rarely get opportunities like this, so I'm somewhat flattered...
502011.name: Paragon of Celestial Grace

502012.desc: I am honored that you could make time in your busy schedule to accept my invitation... Hmm? There's no need to be so formal? Heehee. Well, the tea happens to be ready now, so please sit down next to me~
502012.name: Pristine Leaves, Rich Warmth

502018.desc: Commander, thank you for waiting for me. Though I am unworthy of this honor, thank you so much...
502018.name: Coronal Afterglow

502019.desc: There's no need to worry, Commander. I will be fine now. Please allow me to serve you once more in this new form.
502019.name: Yat Sen (Retrofit)

502020.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruiser, Ning Hai
502020.name: Ning Hai

502021.desc: Summer’s all about the beach! And the beach is all about good food! Commander, let’s find something delicious to eat!
502021.name: Summer Hunger

502022.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! I heard that if you pray to the moon today, you’ll become as pretty as the Goddess of the Moon! ...Eh? You’re gonna pray too?
502022.name: Moon Palace Rabbit

502023.desc: We haven't had to worry as much about things like food since we joined the fleet, but that doesn't mean we can just throw money around...! Anyway, I'm the older of the "Dragon Sisters," Ning Hai! Great to be here!
502023.name: Dragon Sisters! -N

502024.desc: Commander, what are you spacing out for? Over here! They say that you'll have good fortune if you give this thing a shake!
502024.name: Springtime Sojourn

502025.desc: Yat Sen said this look would be best for a party, but, is it really okay? I'm not used to having my hair down like this...
502025.name: Gorgeous Violet

502026.desc: Good boy. Chew thoroughly before you swallow. I never thought I'd help with a charity event for nature, but Da Bao's made a lot of new friends because of it. Keep up the good work, Commander and Ping!
502026.name: Da Bao's Friend!

502029.desc: Yes! … this feels good. Thank you, Commander. In order to live up to your expectations, from now on, I will be more serious around you, Commander. Hey, don't run!
502029.name: Ning Hai (Retrofit)

502030.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruser, Ping Hai
502030.name: Ping Hai

502031.desc: Compared to pork buns, shaved ice is tastier. Compared to shaved ice, fireworks are prettier. Compared to fireworks, what I care for the most is...
502031.name: Summer Vacation

502032.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander! Mooncakes, pomegranates, and osmanthus cakes... what a wonderful holiday!
502032.name: Osmanthus Moon Rabbit

502033.desc: Big sister says that even though we have some money now, we still have to save as much as we can. Um... Anyway, I'm the younger "Dragon Sister," Ping Hai. Erm... I'm kind of hungry. Do you maybe have something to eat?
502033.name: Dragon Sisters! -P

502034.desc: The Sakura Empire has lots of delicious food that I've never tried before! Yeah! It's a great place!
502034.name: Great Gourmet Expedition

502035.desc: There's always a lot of delicious food at these parties! But, my sister said I'm not allowed to have any cake until everyone's gotten their slice... Baobao, let's be on our best behavior!
502035.name: Delicious Crimson

502036.desc: Cheese! That came out looking good! Hehehe~ I'm really glad to be a part of this charity event for nature, along with you and my sister! Baobao is really glad too!
502036.name: Baobao's Buddy!

502039.desc: Hi~ya! Hmm... this feels... nothing special. Baobao looks happy though... Never mind, Commander, Ping Hai is hungry!
502039.name: Ping Hai (Retrofit)

502040.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Ying Swei.
502040.name: Ying Swei

502041.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I've come to deliver you blessings for this coming year... Next, you're going to ask for a red envelope, right? Hehe, just teasing~
502041.name: Snowy Pine's Warmth

502042.desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Chao Ho and I are preparing for this year's Spring Festival, and as you can see... we're in the middle of a little "intermission." Hehe, don't worry, there's nothing you need to help out with. Just take a seat over there and enjoy the show~
502042.name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse I

502050.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Chao Ho.
502050.name: Chao Ho

502051.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! This red envelope is my gift to you... after all, that's my responsibility as a big sister! Anyway, hurry up and take it!
502051.name: Plum Blossom's Illumination

502052.desc: Happy... New Year... Commander... Gah, this isn't the time for pleasantries! And you, help me catch the dumb fluffball that ran off with our ornaments! Jeez, why is this happening when I'm in the middle of getting ready for the Spring Festival?!
502052.name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse II

502070.desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Tien.
502070.name: Hai Tien

502071.desc: What a serendipitous meeting this is, Commander. I was simply searching for a place where I could leisurely enjoy my poetry manuscript. Since fate has brought both of us here, why don't we accompany each other for a while?
502071.name: Verse-Weaver at the Water's Edge

502072.desc: Through dance of gossamer silk, the apsaras' grace soars... Oh, I'm simply reciting something I just happened to pick up on. What do you think, Commander? If I've captured your attention, I suppose this was worth our while~
502072.name: Soaring Apsaras

502073.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting. It took quite some time to prepare my dress as well as this lantern... Yes, when you said we would go on a "night stroll," I made some preparations in accordance to what my ancestors once did. Now then, shall we set off?
502073.name: Autumn Night of Wandering Spirits

502080.desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Chi.
502080.name: Hai Chi

502081.desc: Look, Commander! I've become a goddess from the Dragon Empery's folklore! Hehehe! Let me perform for you a song and dance number I just learned!
502081.name: A Dance Among the Lotuses

502090.desc: CNT Shipyard 1,800-ton small protected cruiser – Chi An.
502090.name: Chi An

502091.desc: May blessings reach you this coming spring. Hm? My outfit? Heehee. Since the ever-so-busy Commander came to see me on this special occasion, I naturally had to put in some effort too– Now then, set aside all your worries, and come enjoy this wonderful evening with me~♪
502091.name: Lanternlit Stroll

504010.desc: 1913 Naval Expansion Project 26,000-ton battlecruiser – Huan Ch'ang.
504010.name: Huan Ch'ang

504011.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. Hmm? I look a bit different from usual? Why of course, it's because it was chosen to suit your tastes by none other than Chi An. Even this mask is brand new. I look "like a fairy from the sacred mountains," you say? I wonder... who taught you to say something like that?
504011.name: Dance Beneath the Moonlight

506011.desc: You're here, Commander, just as promised. How do you like the atmosphere in here? Hehe, take a seat and enjoy the tea slowly. After all, we have plenty of time~
506011.name: Vestibule of Wonders

506012.desc: Oh my, if it isn't the Commander... Have you also come to escape the heat? What a serendipitous meeting... Or, did you perhaps have some other goal in mind? Heehee...
506012.name: Cerulean Ripples

506019.desc: Just as promised, I present myself before you in a brand new form. Heehee... Since we have plenty of time, why don't you come take a seat, enjoy the fragrance of tea with me, and envision our future?
506019.name: Chen Hai (Retrofit)

506021.desc: I am Hwah Jah, now in zombie form. It is an honor to see you– hmm? What's wrong, Commander? Everyone else is getting dressed up for the occasion, so I figured I'd get in on the action too... Is there something wrong with that?
506021.name: The Festive Undead

519011.desc: I see, so this is how you're supposed to knead dough... Hmm? Commander? As you can see, I'm currently trying to make baozi. Would you like to help out?
519011.name: Tender White Jade

520000.desc: 鞍山级驱逐舰1号舰—鞍山，舷号101
520000.name: 导驱type20测试机

521000.desc: 鞍山级驱逐舰1号舰—鞍山，舷号101
521000.name: 导驱type21测试机

599011.desc: Pheeew! I just love blue skies and a fair ocean breeze. Since you're already here, Commander, set aside all the boring paperwork and business stuff, and come enjoy the waves!
599011.name: Union Between Sea and Sky

599018.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. So, how's my new look? It's got me a bit embarrassed... But, well, all that matters is that you like it.
599018.name: Red Paeonia

601021.desc: Lady Veneto advised me to enjoy my time off by changing into something befitting the occasion... Um, Commander, I d-don't look strange, do I?
601021.name: Refreshing Sundress

601032.desc: "To refuse a fair signorina's invitation would be most uncouth"... Hehe~ Now, Commander, would you like to partake in some refreshments? Rest assured, they're all non-alcoholic♪
601032.name: Fair Lady's Invitation

601041.desc: It's way too crowded on the beach... I'd much rather be– Oh, Commander? Are you not good with crowded places either...?
601041.name: Lonesome Beachfarer

601051.desc: Libeccio's heading towards the sea! Commander, let's go to where all the excitement is!
601051.name: Beachbound Southwestern Wind!

601061.desc: I know this one! It's that Sakura Empire watermelon-smashing game! Just put the melon over there, Commander! ...Relax, it'll be fine! Have some faith in my navigator's intuition! Ready? Then let's go!
601061.name: To a Smashing Voyage!

601071.desc: *yawn*... Nothing's impossible when you've got Captain Pompey... Hmm? Commander? Wait, I fell asleep? Seems I did... Drat, I forgot what I even came here for...
601071.name: Quaver Daydream

601081.desc: Found you, Commander! How would you grade this outfit of mine? ...No, no, I wasn't asking if it looked cute or pretty, I wanted to know if I was wearing it right in the first place! You know what though, I think I'll take those compliments~
601081.name: Vivacious Vivace

601091.desc: Eek! Wh-why are you guys tugging at my stockings... P-please stop that... C-Commander, please... Hurry and come help me! Waah...
601091.name: Backstage Blunders

601100.desc: Capitani Romani-class large destroyer – Attilio Regolo.
601100.name: Attilio Regolo

601101.desc: Welcome to my humble abode! Bunnies, kitty-cats, and the Commander... The gang's all here! Today's tale is gonna be a wild one!
601101.name: Castle of Inspiration

602010.desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi.
602010.name: Duca degli Abruzzi

602011.desc: Good evening, Commander. Here to unwind after a day's work, I take it? Even dignitaries desire a bit of luxury sometimes. Hahaha.
602011.name: Lustrous Onyx Sirenetta

602020.desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Giuseppe Garibaldi.
602020.name: Giuseppe Garibaldi

602021.desc: I am the evil swan Odile! Where oh where is my prince? ...Oh, it's you, Commander. My lines aside, pretty good performance, right?
602021.name: Noble Ivory Plumes

603011.desc: The summer's scorching heat is alleviated by the ocean~ Commander, why don't you set aside your worries and... cut loose a bit~?
603011.name: Summer's Hotness?

603021.desc: Phew... It's a perfect day for swimming. Oh my, Commander, did you come to swim too? Or... perhaps you had something else in mind? Ehehe~♪
603021.name: Poolside Coincidence

603031.desc: Zara, how dastardly of you to spike the ball at such a time– Eek?! Commander?! Why are you in a place like that?
603031.name: Seaside Coincidence

603041.desc: Oh my, are you done with your errands already? Surely, you didn't skip work just to eat lunch with... Ah, sorry for doubting you. Alright, let's go. Trento is waiting for us.
603041.name: Rooftop Lunch Break

603042.desc: Whew... I'm getting dizzy... I'll rest in the breeze for a moment. You okay, Commander? Step out if it's too hot. See, someone will worry about you...
603042.name: Amore Termico

603051.desc: I've never had a knack for dancing or exercise unlike Zara and her sisters... but if asked, I will dance as best as I can! Please keep your eyes on me, Commander!
603051.name: A Flutter in the Moment

603052.desc: So... The premise is that you and I were shipwrecked and ended up on a desert island... Is that right, Commander? I see... But if we weren't actually shipwrecked... what is this treasure, then?
603052.name: Tempting Treasure

603061.desc: These stockings are so annoying to wear... Mmrgh... *sigh*. You can't give up already, Gorizia. If you want the Commander's attention... this is what you have to do!
603061.name: Unrequited Office Love?

605011.desc: Nngh, haah... It's awfully sunny today... How long was I asleep, Commander? Oh, it's already lunchtime? In that case, I'll get started on some food. Would you like something as well?
605011.name: The Flower of La Spezia

605021.desc: A visit to the beach with me? Then you must try your hardest to stand out. Otherwise the eyes of the world will be on me alone.
605021.name: The Glory of Naples

605022.desc: Welcome to Littorio's personal suite. Are you here to issue me a challenge of who can romance the most girls? Hahahah, I'm joking of course! There'd be no fun in a game I would win every single time.
605022.name: Calabria Aurea

605023.desc: Hello there. You'll have to forgive the loungewear; I have scarcely any reason to wear extravagant clothes in my private space away from the public eye.
605023.name: Lounging Emerald

605024.desc: Talk about bad luck, we're caught in a rainstorm right now. Unfortunately, it seems we'll have to wait it out here, Commander.
605024.name: Sitting in the Rain

605031.desc: You seem to have known that I would be here. Then stay and spend the night with me. Just the two of us.
605031.name: White Heron of Darkest Night

605050.desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Conte di Cavour.
605050.name: Conte di Cavour

605051.desc: Commander, take this. Good, for the time being, you are a now a disciple under my command. It is time for us to mete out punishment to the unruly.
605051.name: Fierce Beachside Battle

605060.desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Giulio Cesare.
605060.name: Giulio Cesare

605061.desc: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!
605061.name: Fitness Master

605062.desc: Tired already? For goodness' sake, I thought you'd be more reliable than this. Don't go burning all your energy at once, we still have a whole day of recreation ahead of us.
605062.name: High Tide Under the Sunlight

605071.desc: "I'm your stewardess, Andrea Doria, here to ensure you have a pleasant flight"... Did I sound natural, Commander? ...Still a bit on the stiff side, huh? *sigh*, this job really isn't easy for first-timers...
605071.name: Have a Safe Flight

607011.desc: Good day, my Commander. We have the day off to enjoy the sea breeze and the ocean waves~ Hehe, would you like to help yourself to some fruit?
607011.name: Sardegnian Shallows and Sunshine

607012.desc: Oh, my Commander? I didn't expect to meet you here! Fortune smiles upon me today. Hehe~ If you have a minute to spare, would you care to join me for a cup of tea?
607012.name: A Sip of Sardegnian Elegance

607021.desc: Seems school uniforms are all the hype. Veneto picked this one out for me. What are you dressed as, Commander? A teacher? A classmate?
607021.name: Languid Librarian

608011.desc: Hehe, hehehehe... We have this little c-corner of the beach all to ourselves... Now, what should we do first... Hehehehe...
608011.name: Shady Seaside

608021.desc: Here to watch me rehearse just like these deer, Commander? Isn't it wonderful being surrounded by the beauty of nature? For a performance based on a fable such as this one, ambiance is key. Ehehe~♪
608021.name: Riverside Pirouette

699011.desc: Me? Serve as your maid? Oho! That's more like it, Commander! How magnificent and ambitious of you! ...Only temporarily? And you're content with that?
699011.name: The Queen of Hearts

701021.desc: Comrade Commander, are you here to see my room? Hm? That Шутки isn't funny? Then how about... did my room come to see you, comrade Commander?
701021.name: Bad Bunny Behind Bars

701022.desc: Hmm... If I tweak Królik around a bit like this... But, it'll probably be a problem if I don't finish this in one go... Guess I'll think about it while I eat. Mhm.
701022.name: Bunny Remodeling Plan?

701023.desc: Our shift starts now. Królik, Pirožkí, Manjuus – form up! Let us realize our Manjuu comrades' dreams!
701023.name: Shadowy Syndicate Showdown

701024.desc: *burp*... Now I think I get the appeal of tea. Why is the cup so small, though? Do you have a bigger one on hand, Comrade Commander?
701024.name: Tea Party with Królik

701025.desc: Uughh... Ooohh... Królik is melting... *gasp*! I'm getting lightheaded... Comrade Commander, fetch me some ice...
701025.name: Bunny in the Banya

701031.desc: You've violated the Minsk Protocol, comrade! Therefore, the sentence appropriate for you is imprisonment! Until when? Obviously, until your jailor is satisfied~♪
701031.name: Thunderous Jailor

701041.desc: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?
701041.name: The Bound Cruiser

701042.desc: Urrk... Who dares disturb Tashkent's slumber? ...Oh, it's you, dear comrade? Um, in that case... I can always get more rest later. Is something the matter?
701042.name: The Blue Snoozer

701050.desc: How do you like my outfit, dear comrade? ...Is that so? After all of Tashkent's work to become an idol, that's how you react? Hmph. Just you wait. My next concert will rock your socks off.
701050.name: Tashkent μ

701061.desc: It sucks not being able to play in the snow... Oh well! I'll play some games instead! Commander, let's play something fun together!
701061.name: No Snow No Life

701071.desc: Wh-who gave you the right to just barge in? ...I did? Huh. Well, seeing as you're here, I guess we could read a book together. Mm, that's all.
701071.name: A Daytime Delight is in a Book

701081.desc: Comrade! The morning is already here! Look how high the sun is in the sky!! C'mon, a wonderful day is calling to us~!!
701081.name: Morning's Beckoning

701091.desc: Yes, these data and results are quite interesting... Though they mean nothing to me! I am a genius mechanic, not an analyst! Ahh-ha-ha-haah!
701091.name: The Machinery of Life

701101.desc: Seeing you here puts me at ease. I know this stakeout will go smoothly as long as you're here. Mhm, all is fine.
701101.name: Backstreet Silver Sonata

701102.desc: Since you're a beginner at this, Commander, let me show you the ropes. Somehow... it feels like I skate better than usual when you're around. I'm pretty good at ice skating, aren't I? This... should be fine, right?
701102.name: Víla of the Crystal Lake

702011.desc: "I am Avrora, the princess bound within this tower by a cruel fate... My beloved, please come for me soon..."
702011.name: Shackled Saule

702012.desc: "Muahaha... Now, these streets belong to me..." Sorry, I bit my tongue... Hmm, getting into this role is quite difficult for me after all.
702012.name: Not Cut Out For This?

702021.desc: What kinda exercise is this?! Nobody said I'd become a dang showpiece! Come on, get this thing off me, NOW!
702021.name: Caged Minx

702022.desc: Mmmh~ I sure could get used to this life~ Oh, Commander, thanks for being my gofer~♪ Ah, you can leave the cherries right over here!
702022.name: Sweet Cherry Memories

702023.desc: Aaand send DM to Rossiya... Finally you showed up, Commander! So, where are you taking me, hmm?
702023.name: Chic and Cheeky

702024.desc: Happy Valentine's Day~♪ Did you come here to enjoy my chocolate? Then, try guessing where I hid my chocolate – if you get it right, I'll give it to you~♪ Is it here... or maybe over here? Ahahaha~♡
702024.name: Mercurial Chocolate Love

702029.desc: My retrofitting is done! Look forward to seeing how both my cuteness and combat potential have been upgraded!
702029.name: Pamiat' Merkuria (Retrofit)

702031.desc: Commander, what's going on? Did I... do something wrong...? This was all just... meant to be an exercise, right?
702031.name: The Captive Cavalier

702032.desc: Phew... Oh my, Commander, I'm sorry I didn't welcome you at the door. You don't have to be so tense - I already know not to try doing anything weird with you. Hehe~
702032.name: White Cavalier's Respite

702033.desc: You've been looking for me? Heehee, sorry if I made you worry, I just had to feel the night breeze in my hair for a bit. Why don't you stay and enjoy it with me?
702033.name: Indigo & Lantern-Lit Summer Night

702034.desc: Why are you here... Oh, that was rude of me to ask. Maybe you just wanted a change of scenery, or you were drawn by the music. Or maybe my feelings have reached you... I think I like the sound of that one the most. Hehehe.
702034.name: Melody of the White Cavalier

702041.desc: Comrade Commander, you've come at a good time. I've recently taken a liking to this blend of coffee. Want some as well? No need to be shy.
702041.name: Blend R

702042.desc: Halt! You have nowhere left to run!! ...Well done, Comrade Commander, what a thrilling chase we had on our hands! What, you think I'm well-suited for this job? You tease too much, bahaha!
702042.name: Drifting Justice

702043.desc: ...Hmph! Just short of a new personal best, huh? But make no mistake, Comrade Commander. Keep watching me and your patience WILL be rewarded with a breathtaking record!
702043.name: High Jump Star

702051.desc: ...Thus marks the end of this tune. The Dragon Empery has graciously allowed me to perform in their Spring Festival celebration. Are you here to listen, Commander? In that case... How did you like the song? Heehee.
702051.name: Maestro of Sterling Strings

702061.desc: ...Achoo! Uhh, good morning... Snow? Yeah, it is snowing today... Woah, it's really coming down hard... Ahaha~
702061.name: Sceneries of Pure Snow

702071.desc: Comrade Commander, is the bath to your liking? I'm glad. Heehee, it's a good thing I trusted that "Top 10 Dates for Snowy Days" article and chose this secluded hot spring.
702071.name: Devoted as the Warm Snow

703011.desc: What, you've never seen the inside of a shipgirl's room? It's not like you're here on official business, so stop standing around already. Find a place to sit and relax.
703011.name: Nostalgic Pilsner

703012.desc: You've reached the Bureau of Investigation... Oh boy, another case. Commander, finish up your paperwork ASAP. We've got witnesses to interview.
703012.name: As You Say, Ma'am!

703021.desc: This steamy hot spring... is a rather novel experience. I left a spot for you, so come sit down already – Wait, why haven't you taken your clothes off yet?
703021.name: Lone Wolf Amid the Steam

705011.desc: You have my thanks for this exercise, comrade! I shall gladly carry out the important duty of judge, jury, and rehabilitator!
705011.name: Imposing Warden

705012.desc: ...Bwahaah! I've had all kinds of liquor, but nothing beats the stuff back home! Comrade, let's have a toast to the coming off-duty days!
705012.name: Keeper of the Firewater

705041.desc: To pass the time by proactively reading, or by passively enjoying the company of others... Ah, good morning, Comrade, I've been expecting you. Hahaha!
705041.name: Relaxation Stratagem

705051.desc: "Situation normal in all sectors of the facility..." Oh, it is you. I was just giving Minsk the daily report. Do you have something?
705051.name: The Lackadaisical Lookout

705061.desc: Your choice treasure now belongs to master thief Arkhangelsk! Think you can arrest me? Then stop gawking and come get me!
705061.name: Grandiose Getaway

705071.desc: Phew... This is... Comrade Commander? Fancy meeting you at this time of night. Me? Heh, heheheheh... You wouldn't believe me if I said I got too drunk and went in first, would you?
705071.name: More than a Little Drunk

707011.desc: Volga here. I'm currently tracking an important witness. *gurgle* ...Is my stomach rumbling because this AR game requires so much stamina? Ugh, lost track of the witness just now...
707011.name: An Irresistible AR Adventure

718011.desc: Listen up, assholes! We have you surrounded! I'm Kronshtadt, squad leader of the Northern Parliament Special Forces! You have only one option: come out with your hands in the air and surrender!
718011.name: Begin the Rush!

799011.desc: Oh? What made you come over here instead of heading down to the beach? Surely you didn't ditch your friends on a hard-earned day off just to see me? But, I don't mind. It's called a day off because you get to decide how to spend your time.
799011.name: Seaside Sunset

801021.desc: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?
801021.name: Fleur Blanche

801022.desc: Even though I'm an Iris Libre squire, I'm currently working hard to have a rich student life. Um... maybe this is a bit too laid back?
801022.name: École de Chevalier

801023.desc: Good evening, Commander. I am currently enjoying the party in the company of my friends, as my duties as a squire entail. Um... I've had a bit too much to drink? R-really...?
801023.name: Feast of Champagne

801028.desc: At long last, this wonderful day is here. It feels like I'm dreaming... I'm so happy, I just... Forgive me, I promised myself I wouldn't cry... I, Forbin the squire, shall remain by your side for the rest of my life!
801028.name: Fleur de Mariée

801029.desc: My hard work has finally paid off! Commander, thank you for your guidance all this time! I'll return the favor by bringing you even more honors in battle!
801029.name: Forbin (Retrofit)

801031.desc: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!
801031.name: Summery Temeraire!

801032.desc: How do I look? These pajamas are super cute, aren't they? Ehehe, I really like this one! It even matches with Opiniâtre's!
801032.name: Dreamy Dolce

801041.desc: It is said that the summertime sea holds an extraordinary enchantment over people... but the only supernatural thing I'm feeling is this accursed heat... Am I missing something?
801041.name: Beachside Magician

801070.desc: Le Fantasque-class large destroyer - Le Terrible.
801070.name: Le Terrible

801071.desc: Zzz... Commander...? Sorry... for showing you this unsightly side of mine... I'm just, not a morning person... Zzzzz...
801071.name: Silence, Slumber, and Solace

801072.desc: How goes your day, Commander? Hehe, are you looking for my clever sister, Le Malin? If so, you would do well to search somewhere less... popular~♪
801072.name: Sunlight, Seaspray, and Sanctity

801081.desc: H-h-halt, intruder! Thou art intruding in the domain of an Iris Libre Templar Knight, a crime punishable by... Eek! I'm begging you, spare my life! ...It's you, Lord Commander?!
801081.name: The Noble Knight's Last Stand

801082.desc: Enjoying sweet pastries in a lovely dress – heehee, such bliss! ...I care not how unbecoming this is of a knight! I saved these desserts for my holiday! Let me enjoy myself, would you!
801082.name: Sugary Sabbatical

802011.desc: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~
802011.name: Côte d'Azur
